WEBVTT

1
00:00:17.583 --> 00:00:22.416
A TRUE STORY BY NORMA RISMA

2
00:00:25.833 --> 00:00:30.666
[Norma] Marriage
is supposed to be once-in-a-lifetime.

3
00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:33.583
Unfortunately,

4
00:00:34.541 --> 00:00:36.875
not all mistakes

5
00:00:37.875 --> 00:00:39.625
or betrayals

6
00:00:39.708 --> 00:00:40.541
[camera click]

7
00:00:41.875 --> 00:00:44.875
[crying]
can be forgiven by the word "Sorry".

8
00:00:44.958 --> 00:00:50.791
[pensive music]

9
00:00:50.875 --> 00:00:54.000
Like what happened in my marriage.

10
00:01:00.208 --> 00:01:01.958
The betrayal,

11
00:01:02.041 --> 00:01:03.166
[quiet sob]

12
00:01:03.250 --> 00:01:06.250
it was my husband who did it.

13
00:01:08.125 --> 00:01:11.125
With someone I should have respected…

14
00:01:11.208 --> 00:01:13.791
PRESIDING JUDGE

15
00:01:13.875 --> 00:01:17.666
…and the one who should love me the most.

16
00:01:17.750 --> 00:01:20.958
[dramatic music builds]

17
00:01:21.041 --> 00:01:25.333
[sobbing]

18
00:01:35.958 --> 00:01:38.166
[light background music]

19
00:01:38.250 --> 00:01:40.625
A FEW MONTHS EARLIER

20
00:01:42.041 --> 00:01:44.625
[Ummi] Our topic this morning is…

21
00:01:44.708 --> 00:01:47.833
"The Role of Mothers in Islam"

22
00:01:47.916 --> 00:01:49.541
Kindly have your notes ready.

23
00:01:49.625 --> 00:01:51.375
Let's learn together later, shall we?

24
00:01:54.916 --> 00:01:56.791
You're just walking around aimlessly!

25
00:01:56.875 --> 00:01:58.583
They haven't arrived yet, Mom!

26
00:02:00.458 --> 00:02:04.416
Norma has set aside one for you, Mom.

27
00:02:04.500 --> 00:02:06.375
[Ummi] Everyone ready?

28
00:02:06.458 --> 00:02:08.500
As the saying goes…

29
00:02:09.375 --> 00:02:13.625
Heaven lies under the feet

30
00:02:13.708 --> 00:02:14.833
of mothers.

31
00:02:14.916 --> 00:02:18.208
Mother is the first school,

32
00:02:18.291 --> 00:02:20.875
and also primary for her children.

33
00:02:20.958 --> 00:02:23.708
[Ummi] So if a mother succeeds…

34
00:02:23.791 --> 00:02:26.583
…to raise her children to be good humans,

35
00:02:26.666 --> 00:02:29.416
the society will also
become a strong society.

36
00:02:29.500 --> 00:02:31.458
Mom, can I go out for a while?

37
00:02:31.541 --> 00:02:35.708
[Ummi] Because a mother's love
is always easy.

38
00:02:35.791 --> 00:02:37.083
Where is Anton?

39
00:02:37.166 --> 00:02:38.708
He's sick, Boss!

40
00:02:38.791 --> 00:02:40.000
Nauseous!

41
00:02:40.083 --> 00:02:41.625
Have you told him to
seek medical treatment?

42
00:02:41.708 --> 00:02:44.500
Yes, Boss, he has been absent
for a few days now.

43
00:02:44.583 --> 00:02:47.916
-Maybe he’s been cursed, Sir.
-Hey, watch your mouth!

44
00:02:48.458 --> 00:02:50.166
BANTEN GRAND MOSQUE'S ISLAMIC STUDY

45
00:02:50.250 --> 00:02:51.333
[Boss] Stop!

46
00:02:51.416 --> 00:02:57.041
[light background music]

47
00:02:57.125 --> 00:02:59.125
That's why you should learn to drive!

48
00:02:59.208 --> 00:03:02.083
If Anton is absent like this,
you don't have to wait for me.

49
00:03:02.166 --> 00:03:03.666
[van driver] That woman has arrived, Boss!

50
00:03:05.750 --> 00:03:09.416
My apologies, I was delayed
due to an unforeseen issue.

51
00:03:09.500 --> 00:03:11.208
Fine Sir, the main thing is
you've arrived safely.

52
00:03:11.291 --> 00:03:12.125
Is everything ready?

53
00:03:12.208 --> 00:03:13.916
All done, but there's still one more left.

54
00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:14.833
-Okay.
-This is so heavy.

55
00:03:14.916 --> 00:03:17.833
Miss, I'm sorry for making
you wait so long.

56
00:03:17.916 --> 00:03:19.375
It’s okay!

57
00:03:20.458 --> 00:03:24.708
These are for mothers and kids
of our religious study group.

58
00:03:24.791 --> 00:03:28.666
-[teacher calling] Calm down!
-[children shouting]

59
00:03:28.750 --> 00:03:31.083
-Well, you know.
-Easy… Easy…!

60
00:03:31.166 --> 00:03:34.083
-Kids, take it easy!
-[children clamouring]

61
00:03:34.166 --> 00:03:35.041
Children…

62
00:03:35.625 --> 00:03:37.250
[Norma] You're welcome!

63
00:03:37.333 --> 00:03:41.041
-When you have one, go study again!
-[children] Thank you, Miss!

64
00:03:41.125 --> 00:03:42.583
-What is that?
-Me!

65
00:03:42.666 --> 00:03:44.000
-Here you go.
-Thank you.

66
00:03:44.083 --> 00:03:46.416
Yeah. Share them, okay? Here.

67
00:03:46.500 --> 00:03:48.125
Is everything done, Miss?

68
00:03:48.791 --> 00:03:49.916
Yes, it’s done.

69
00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:52.166
-Thank you, Sir.
-My pleasure!

70
00:03:52.250 --> 00:03:54.625
And thank you to the driver as well!

71
00:03:54.708 --> 00:03:57.333
Oh right, let me introduce
my boss, Mr. Irfan.

72
00:03:57.416 --> 00:04:00.833
If it weren't for him,
I could go back and forth by motorcycle.

73
00:04:00.916 --> 00:04:02.958
[driver] It took an hour!

74
00:04:03.583 --> 00:04:04.541
[Irfan] Irfan!

75
00:04:04.625 --> 00:04:06.333
[light background music]

76
00:04:06.416 --> 00:04:07.291
[umm sound]

77
00:04:11.458 --> 00:04:14.333
Hey, I think we've met before, right?

78
00:04:14.416 --> 00:04:16.250
You seem familiar.

79
00:04:16.333 --> 00:04:17.875
He's hitting on you!

80
00:04:17.958 --> 00:04:21.291
Ah, i’m being serious! Where did we meet?

81
00:04:21.375 --> 00:04:22.791
What did you say your name was?

82
00:04:22.875 --> 00:04:26.833
[embarrassed cough] Sorry,
I haven't said my name yet.

83
00:04:26.916 --> 00:04:28.208
I’m Norma, Sir.

84
00:04:28.916 --> 00:04:29.916
Norma from SMANDA?

85
00:04:30.000 --> 00:04:32.291
Are you from SMANDA too?

86
00:04:32.375 --> 00:04:34.583
[shows ID card]

87
00:04:34.666 --> 00:04:37.250
I'm Irfan Wardana, Social Three!

88
00:04:37.333 --> 00:04:40.291
-You’re head of pencak silat, right?
-[chuckle] I'm the vice-chairman.

89
00:04:40.375 --> 00:04:41.916
-Oh!
-[giggles]

90
00:04:42.000 --> 00:04:43.125
[Norma] This shows…

91
00:04:43.208 --> 00:04:48.041
…how important a mother's
role is in Islam.

92
00:04:50.125 --> 00:04:52.333
Miss, we're sorry,
we have to take our leave now.

93
00:04:52.916 --> 00:04:53.875
Can I have your phone?

94
00:04:53.958 --> 00:04:57.541
[startled breath] No way, the boss
is asking for a phone?

95
00:04:57.625 --> 00:04:58.875
Just buy one!

96
00:04:58.958 --> 00:05:01.750
Your phone number, I mean. May I have it?

97
00:05:01.833 --> 00:05:03.000
[shy umm sound]

98
00:05:03.916 --> 00:05:07.000
No, thank you, Sir. I have to go now.

99
00:05:07.083 --> 00:05:07.916
Peace be upon you.

100
00:05:08.000 --> 00:05:10.625
-Peace be upon you.
-Miss, sorry, you forgot this.

101
00:05:10.708 --> 00:05:14.000
Oh, the staff here will
take care of it later.

102
00:05:14.083 --> 00:05:15.666
-His name is Mr. Unim.
-Okay.

103
00:05:16.208 --> 00:05:18.500
-Peace be upon you.
-Peace be upon you.

104
00:05:28.791 --> 00:05:31.875
Hey, let’s get to work!

105
00:05:31.958 --> 00:05:35.708
[upbeat music]

106
00:05:35.791 --> 00:05:36.791
[train horn and track noise]

107
00:05:44.000 --> 00:05:45.958
-Sir, the pedicab, please.
-[driver] Yes, Ma'am.

108
00:05:46.041 --> 00:05:50.875
[Norma] Mom, do you know Rika,
my old college friend?

109
00:05:50.958 --> 00:05:54.583
She now works at SD Tunas Bangsa.

110
00:05:54.666 --> 00:05:55.583
[Mom grunts]

111
00:05:55.666 --> 00:05:58.208
She asked me to work there, Mom…

112
00:05:58.291 --> 00:06:02.583
…to replace a religious teacher there.

113
00:06:03.291 --> 00:06:07.708
Their teacher just resigned
after marital leave.

114
00:06:07.791 --> 00:06:11.458
What do you think if I move there?

115
00:06:11.541 --> 00:06:13.083
The salary is quite good.

116
00:06:13.166 --> 00:06:16.708
You barely help me at the stall
while working at the TPA,

117
00:06:17.500 --> 00:06:19.166
why do you think you can be a teacher?

118
00:06:19.250 --> 00:06:23.208
Well, I'm pretty sure, Mom.
I will arrange the time later.

119
00:06:23.291 --> 00:06:25.583
It would be a pity to miss it.

120
00:06:26.833 --> 00:06:27.708
May I?

121
00:06:32.208 --> 00:06:33.416
[Norma] Who's here, Mom?

122
00:06:34.041 --> 00:06:36.125
-[Norma] Peace be upon you.
-[Mom] Peace be upon you.

123
00:06:36.791 --> 00:06:38.750
[Father] Peace be upon you

124
00:06:41.333 --> 00:06:42.291
Dad!

125
00:06:42.375 --> 00:06:48.250
[quiet music]

126
00:07:00.375 --> 00:07:01.583
Dad!

127
00:07:02.333 --> 00:07:05.666
-My dear!
-Why didn’t you tell me before?

128
00:07:06.291 --> 00:07:08.125
-Surprise!
-[happy laugh]

129
00:07:08.208 --> 00:07:10.250
If I had known,
I would’ve bought you Bang Cukit's Apem!

130
00:07:10.333 --> 00:07:11.375
[Norma] Let’s see ya!

131
00:07:11.458 --> 00:07:13.958
[Norma chuckling]
Koh Akin gave you a day off?

132
00:07:14.458 --> 00:07:16.791
[Dad] Koh Akin's sibling
is having a wedding.

133
00:07:16.875 --> 00:07:20.375
He is busy with the wedding,
so the shop is closed now!

134
00:07:20.458 --> 00:07:21.333
[Norma laughs]

135
00:07:21.416 --> 00:07:23.541
[Norma] Alright,
I'll take the food to the kitchen.

136
00:07:23.625 --> 00:07:25.625
[Dad] It's okay, I'll take care of it!

137
00:07:29.708 --> 00:07:31.291
I'll be in the back room!

138
00:07:35.625 --> 00:07:39.666
[deep breath]

139
00:07:40.625 --> 00:07:44.208
How’s your mother?

140
00:07:45.000 --> 00:07:47.125
Well, the same…

141
00:07:48.166 --> 00:07:50.041
-The same?
-Yes.

142
00:07:50.625 --> 00:07:51.750
[opening bag]

143
00:07:51.833 --> 00:07:55.458
She still sells chicken noodles
when there are orders.

144
00:07:55.541 --> 00:07:59.375
She tends to keep to herself while free.

145
00:07:59.458 --> 00:08:01.333
[Norma] As if
you don’t know her at all.

146
00:08:01.416 --> 00:08:03.875
Well, I was just asking how she is.

147
00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:08.958
[Norma] Mom!

148
00:08:11.000 --> 00:08:12.416
[door opens]

149
00:08:13.833 --> 00:08:16.666
Mom, come to the town square
with me and Dad!

150
00:08:16.750 --> 00:08:18.083
Come and buy Bang Cukit’s Apem.

151
00:08:18.166 --> 00:08:19.208
You go!

152
00:08:19.291 --> 00:08:22.875
[Norma] Come on, Mom!
We rarely go out together.

153
00:08:22.958 --> 00:08:24.041
Only this once, please!

154
00:08:24.125 --> 00:08:25.208
You should go!

155
00:08:25.291 --> 00:08:27.250
-My dear!
-Yes, Dad?

156
00:08:27.333 --> 00:08:29.875
[Dad] It's okay, let's just go together!

157
00:08:29.958 --> 00:08:31.958
Alright then, I'm going now.

158
00:08:33.250 --> 00:08:36.000
-[Norma] Peace be upon you.
-Peace be upon you.

159
00:08:43.541 --> 00:08:44.583
Let’s go!

160
00:08:44.666 --> 00:08:46.125
BANG CUKIT'S APEM

161
00:08:46.208 --> 00:08:47.166
Here you go.

162
00:08:47.250 --> 00:08:49.250
-Thank you very much.
-Sure.

163
00:08:49.333 --> 00:08:51.208
[Norma] In the name of Allah.

164
00:08:51.291 --> 00:08:56.666
[light music]

165
00:09:00.000 --> 00:09:00.833
Dad…

166
00:09:02.791 --> 00:09:05.416
Dad, why don't you want
to move your job here?

167
00:09:05.500 --> 00:09:08.500
Keep me company, I'm getting lonely.

168
00:09:11.000 --> 00:09:14.416
Well, Dad's livelihood is in Jakarta.

169
00:09:14.500 --> 00:09:18.250
What job would I do if I worked here?

170
00:09:18.916 --> 00:09:20.875
The salary here isn't much either.

171
00:09:20.958 --> 00:09:24.000
It's because you want
to be far from Mom, right?

172
00:09:26.708 --> 00:09:31.041
Once you have a partner, you'll forget me.

173
00:09:31.958 --> 00:09:33.833
You will not be lonely anymore!

174
00:09:34.500 --> 00:09:36.583
No, Dad!

175
00:09:36.666 --> 00:09:40.708
Even if I have a partner,
I'll still be ‘clingy’ to Dad!

176
00:09:40.791 --> 00:09:43.125
-[in English] C-Clingy?
-Clingy.

177
00:09:43.208 --> 00:09:44.083
What is ‘clingy’?

178
00:09:45.708 --> 00:09:48.583
Clingy' means very close!

179
00:09:48.666 --> 00:09:52.583
[traffic] Anyway, I'm not even thinking
about getting a partner yet, Dad…

180
00:09:52.666 --> 00:09:55.958
-…or even married.
-[Dad] Be patient, my dear.

181
00:09:56.041 --> 00:09:59.375
Find a man who is
consistent in his prayers…

182
00:09:59.458 --> 00:10:03.208
…religiously sound, easy to talk with.

183
00:10:03.291 --> 00:10:05.291
Who can make you laugh,

184
00:10:05.375 --> 00:10:08.000
-and be ‘clingy’ with you.
-[Norma chuckles]

185
00:10:08.083 --> 00:10:08.958
Peace be upon you, Norma.

186
00:10:09.041 --> 00:10:11.416
-Peace be upon you.
-Peace be upon you.

187
00:10:11.500 --> 00:10:14.041
-Peace be upon you, Sir.
-Peace be upon you.

188
00:10:15.625 --> 00:10:18.125
I'm Irfan, Norma and I were
in the same high school.

189
00:10:18.208 --> 00:10:19.041
Ah, okay

190
00:10:19.625 --> 00:10:22.833
-Aren't you working today?
-I already finished my morning shift.

191
00:10:22.916 --> 00:10:24.833
My mom told me to buy snacks.

192
00:10:25.500 --> 00:10:27.875
Does Father and Norma
like to buy snacks here?

193
00:10:29.041 --> 00:10:32.083
This is Norma's favourite Apem Cukit.

194
00:10:32.166 --> 00:10:33.916
-Is it good, Sir?
-Indeed!

195
00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:36.791
Okay, I'll get this packed for my mom,
hopefully she'll enjoy it.

196
00:10:36.875 --> 00:10:40.041
I'm going to buy noodles first,
sorry for bothering you.

197
00:10:40.625 --> 00:10:42.875
-[Irfan] Peace be upon you.
-Peace be upon you.

198
00:10:42.958 --> 00:10:45.166
CHICKEN NOODLES - MR. SUNTO'S MEATBALLS

199
00:10:46.291 --> 00:10:48.083
[light music]

200
00:10:48.166 --> 00:10:51.958
We were just talking about a 'partner',
and there he is.

201
00:10:52.041 --> 00:10:53.958
What?

202
00:10:54.041 --> 00:10:56.041
He’s quite polite too.

203
00:10:57.083 --> 00:10:58.166
And handsome too!

204
00:10:58.250 --> 00:11:01.375
-Dad, stop it!
-You could be ‘clingy’ with him.

205
00:11:02.625 --> 00:11:05.750
[Norma] After finishing
reciting the Quran, what should we say?

206
00:11:05.833 --> 00:11:09.375
[children] Thank you God!

207
00:11:09.458 --> 00:11:11.208
Be careful on your way home.

208
00:11:11.291 --> 00:11:12.708
Put on your shoes.

209
00:11:12.791 --> 00:11:13.916
RIYADHUL HIKMAH QURAN EDUCATION CENTER

210
00:11:14.000 --> 00:11:15.250
-Don't…
-Ouch!

211
00:11:15.333 --> 00:11:17.291
…fight over the shoes.

212
00:11:17.375 --> 00:11:19.000
-[children] Peace be upon you.
-[Norma] Peace be upon you too.

213
00:11:19.083 --> 00:11:21.125
[Irfan] We've met a few times, right?

214
00:11:21.708 --> 00:11:25.250
Maybe this is a sign that
I can ask for your phone number?

215
00:11:27.708 --> 00:11:31.708
If we keep meeting so often,
we don't need phone numbers, right?

216
00:11:32.416 --> 00:11:34.375
Oh, I guess not then.

217
00:11:34.458 --> 00:11:36.708
Well, I'll come here tomorrow!

218
00:11:36.791 --> 00:11:39.333
Maybe next time you'll allow me
to take your phone number.

219
00:11:42.166 --> 00:11:43.416
Peace be upon you.

220
00:11:44.250 --> 00:11:45.666
Peace be upon you.

221
00:11:45.750 --> 00:11:49.166
[upbeat music]

222
00:11:49.250 --> 00:11:51.500
[Irfan] Norma, can I give you a ride home?

223
00:11:52.083 --> 00:11:53.250
-No.
-How about tomorrow?

224
00:11:53.750 --> 00:11:56.625
The day after tomorrow?
The day after the day after tomorrow?

225
00:11:56.708 --> 00:11:58.541
Or after the day after tomorrow?
Maybe even later?

226
00:11:58.625 --> 00:12:01.916
-No!
-Ooh, ooh, ooh!

227
00:12:02.000 --> 00:12:05.458
-Gotcha!
-Auntie, stop it!

228
00:12:05.541 --> 00:12:09.875
I'm your dad's sister,
of course we're the same.

229
00:12:09.958 --> 00:12:10.916
[chuckling]

230
00:12:13.541 --> 00:12:14.583
Excuse me.

231
00:12:20.250 --> 00:12:24.041
Let me ask Mr. Unim first,
so he can take you home.

232
00:12:24.125 --> 00:12:26.166
No need, Ummi,
I'll just go ahead and walk.

233
00:12:26.250 --> 00:12:31.583
Be careful, it's late.
Is it safe for you to go home alone?

234
00:12:31.666 --> 00:12:33.458
-No worries…
-[Irfan] No worries, Ma’am!

235
00:12:33.541 --> 00:12:37.750
-Hey, Irfan!
-May I take Norma home, Ma'am?

236
00:12:38.333 --> 00:12:40.666
Oh, we're not mahram, Ummi!

237
00:12:40.750 --> 00:12:43.416
Let's do it this way,
we're in an emergency.

238
00:12:43.500 --> 00:12:47.916
Irfan, I'm entrusting Norma
to you for her safety.

239
00:12:48.000 --> 00:12:50.750
But I ask you one thing…

240
00:12:50.833 --> 00:12:53.500
-…don't mess around!
-Well noted, Ummi!

241
00:12:53.583 --> 00:12:56.500
This is truly your responsibility,
you can't mess around.

242
00:12:56.583 --> 00:12:58.125
Yes, Ummi!

243
00:12:58.208 --> 00:12:59.458
[music continues playing]

244
00:12:59.541 --> 00:13:02.791
I'm so lucky to have received
this trust from Ummi…

245
00:13:02.875 --> 00:13:04.625
to take you home.

246
00:13:04.708 --> 00:13:07.166
[Norma]
Yeah, just don't disappoint her trust.

247
00:13:09.250 --> 00:13:14.875
[motor trying to start]

248
00:13:14.958 --> 00:13:17.375
[motor engine roaring]

249
00:13:18.750 --> 00:13:20.333
Do you mind walking, okay?

250
00:13:21.416 --> 00:13:26.375
Isn't this the bike you
had back in high school?

251
00:13:27.083 --> 00:13:30.916
I remember you used
to like to speed around with it.

252
00:13:31.000 --> 00:13:34.291
Gosh, you only remember
the bad things about me.

253
00:13:36.375 --> 00:13:39.250
Back then, many girls had a crush on you.

254
00:13:40.583 --> 00:13:41.458
Did you?

255
00:13:43.708 --> 00:13:44.750
No!

256
00:13:47.416 --> 00:13:49.416
Please walk slowly!

257
00:13:49.500 --> 00:13:50.833
We've arrived, Irfan.

258
00:13:55.541 --> 00:13:57.333
-Thank you, Irfan.
-My pleasure.

259
00:13:57.416 --> 00:13:59.583
Wait, Norma.

260
00:14:02.000 --> 00:14:02.958
[Irfan] This is for you.

261
00:14:06.125 --> 00:14:06.958
Thanks.

262
00:14:08.083 --> 00:14:09.083
[Irfan sighs]

263
00:14:09.166 --> 00:14:12.083
Can I say hello to your father?

264
00:14:12.166 --> 00:14:14.875
My dad is currently working in Jakarta.

265
00:14:14.958 --> 00:14:16.791
[Irfan] Your Mom?

266
00:14:16.875 --> 00:14:19.666
She's already asleep at this hour.

267
00:14:19.750 --> 00:14:20.583
Go inside, Norma!

268
00:14:22.958 --> 00:14:24.125
[embarrassed grunt] Irfan!

269
00:14:25.166 --> 00:14:26.375
Peace be upon you, Madam!

270
00:14:26.458 --> 00:14:27.875
-I’m Irfan.
-Norma!

271
00:14:33.666 --> 00:14:34.666
I’m sorry.

272
00:14:34.750 --> 00:14:37.125
-Peace be upon you.
-Peace be upon you.

273
00:14:43.208 --> 00:14:44.208
[door closing]

274
00:14:50.083 --> 00:14:53.458
A girl being walked home
by a guy at this hour,

275
00:14:53.541 --> 00:14:55.208
what will the neighbors think?

276
00:14:56.500 --> 00:15:00.041
Why won't you let me have guy friends?

277
00:15:00.125 --> 00:15:03.583
You dare to talk back after
a guy just approached you?

278
00:15:03.666 --> 00:15:06.000
I did not oppose you, Mom.

279
00:15:06.875 --> 00:15:08.625
I was just asking.

280
00:15:08.708 --> 00:15:12.375
[Norma] Why do you never like
any of my male friends?

281
00:15:12.458 --> 00:15:14.708
Is there truly no one good in your eyes?

282
00:15:17.125 --> 00:15:18.416
[Mom sighs]

283
00:15:18.500 --> 00:15:21.583
[Mom] I'm the one who carried
and birthed you.

284
00:15:21.666 --> 00:15:23.166
Raised you.

285
00:15:24.458 --> 00:15:25.750
I know what's best!

286
00:15:26.583 --> 00:15:32.541
[quiet thoughtful music]

287
00:15:34.125 --> 00:15:35.666
[Irfan] Why didn't you reply to my text?

288
00:15:35.750 --> 00:15:37.708
I came to the mosque,
but you were already gone.

289
00:15:37.791 --> 00:15:38.666
What’s wrong?

290
00:15:38.750 --> 00:15:41.875
It's okay,
I just want to go home by myself.

291
00:15:41.958 --> 00:15:43.750
Did your mother scold you?

292
00:15:46.083 --> 00:15:48.458
Seriously? Lying is a sin,
people who lie go to hell.

293
00:15:50.166 --> 00:15:53.375
She doesn't like it. That's it!

294
00:15:53.458 --> 00:15:55.791
You don't need to see me again.

295
00:15:55.875 --> 00:15:58.125
I don't want my mom to scold you.

296
00:15:59.416 --> 00:16:00.416
[hurried grunt]

297
00:16:01.000 --> 00:16:02.625
Wait, wait, Norma!

298
00:16:03.666 --> 00:16:06.625
Perhaps she dislikes me
because she hasn't met me yet.

299
00:16:06.708 --> 00:16:09.791
Who knows, when she does,
she might like me.

300
00:16:11.333 --> 00:16:13.000
I'm such a good
future son-in-law, you know.

301
00:16:14.458 --> 00:16:17.625
-You're talking nonsense!
-Hey, I'm serious!

302
00:16:18.500 --> 00:16:21.166
I'm really sad that you said that.

303
00:16:21.250 --> 00:16:23.291
I thought you would give me a chance.

304
00:16:23.375 --> 00:16:25.833
We haven’t gotten to know
each other that well.

305
00:16:25.916 --> 00:16:28.708
How can we get closer if you
don't respond to my texts?

306
00:16:31.875 --> 00:16:32.916
Norma…

307
00:16:34.291 --> 00:16:36.125
Let's make our relationship serious.

308
00:16:37.500 --> 00:16:38.458
Okay?

309
00:16:38.541 --> 00:16:44.458
[soft music]

310
00:16:48.333 --> 00:16:50.000
Really?

311
00:16:50.916 --> 00:16:54.958
Thank God for answering my prayers!

312
00:16:55.583 --> 00:16:57.541
-Shush
-Why?

313
00:16:57.625 --> 00:16:59.625
Are you serious, you can face my mom?

314
00:17:00.416 --> 00:17:04.083
Is this the feeling of
being cared for by my future wife?

315
00:17:04.875 --> 00:17:06.333
-Hey, I’m serious!
-[chuckling]

316
00:17:07.000 --> 00:17:09.875
We must be ready. In the name of God!

317
00:17:09.958 --> 00:17:11.333
We'll go through this together.

318
00:17:11.416 --> 00:17:17.375
[happy music]

319
00:17:17.458 --> 00:17:18.833
May I help you, Madam?

320
00:17:29.000 --> 00:17:30.541
It’s okay!

321
00:17:32.541 --> 00:17:33.750
[loud knocking]

322
00:17:33.833 --> 00:17:34.916
Mom…

323
00:17:38.708 --> 00:17:41.583
Mom, I have something to give you…

324
00:17:41.666 --> 00:17:44.083
This is from Irfan.

325
00:17:44.625 --> 00:17:46.208
Please accept!

326
00:18:09.375 --> 00:18:11.291
-[Irfan] Auntie!
-Yes?

327
00:18:13.875 --> 00:18:16.833
[engine motor]

328
00:18:20.166 --> 00:18:21.166
-[surprised exclaim]
-[TV gaming]

329
00:18:21.250 --> 00:18:22.416
-Please sit.
-Gosh.

330
00:18:23.166 --> 00:18:25.375
Oh, no. [deep sigh]

331
00:18:25.458 --> 00:18:26.291
Mom…

332
00:18:26.375 --> 00:18:28.000
Yes, Irfan?

333
00:18:28.083 --> 00:18:30.125
[footsteps]

334
00:18:30.208 --> 00:18:33.208
Firza, do you know where
your sister’s birth certificate is?

335
00:18:33.291 --> 00:18:34.375
[Firza] No!

336
00:18:34.458 --> 00:18:36.708
-[footsteps] Mom!
-You're always gaming!

337
00:18:36.791 --> 00:18:39.708
-Peace be upon you, Madam.
-[Irfan's mom] Peace be upon you.

338
00:18:39.791 --> 00:18:41.625
Are you waiting for…

339
00:18:41.708 --> 00:18:42.875
[breath of assent]

340
00:18:42.958 --> 00:18:44.083
Irfan, Madam.

341
00:18:44.166 --> 00:18:46.625
You’re a friend of Irfan?

342
00:18:46.708 --> 00:18:48.416
-[Irfan] Future wife!
-What?

343
00:18:49.083 --> 00:18:52.166
Future wife? Seriously?

344
00:18:52.250 --> 00:18:55.416
Well, praise to God…

345
00:18:55.500 --> 00:18:56.875
…somebody is interested in you.

346
00:18:56.958 --> 00:18:58.833
[Mom] No, I’m kidding, dear!

347
00:18:58.916 --> 00:19:01.041
Sorry, what’s your name?

348
00:19:01.125 --> 00:19:04.541
-[call ringing]
-Peace be upon you, Mira. What’s up?

349
00:19:04.625 --> 00:19:07.416
Please wait a moment,
Irfan has a guest here.

350
00:19:07.500 --> 00:19:09.458
[embarrassed chuckle] Sorry, dear!

351
00:19:10.041 --> 00:19:14.375
This is Mira, Irfan's sister.
She's looking for her birth certificate.

352
00:19:14.458 --> 00:19:17.958
Where is it? [mumbling] I forgot it.

353
00:19:18.041 --> 00:19:20.250
Firza, did you eat already?

354
00:19:20.333 --> 00:19:23.333
I bought you a batagor, don't forget it.

355
00:19:23.416 --> 00:19:24.458
-[Irfan] Mom…
-Well, where is it?

356
00:19:24.541 --> 00:19:26.500
-Mom…
-Ouch, it’s so heavy!

357
00:19:26.583 --> 00:19:29.166
-Mom…
-What now, Irfan?

358
00:19:29.250 --> 00:19:30.875
Go see her, first.

359
00:19:30.958 --> 00:19:32.791
Wait, this is your sister's thing.

360
00:19:32.875 --> 00:19:35.041
Peace be upon you. Mira? Mira?

361
00:19:35.750 --> 00:19:37.625
[Irfan] I'm so sorry about that!

362
00:19:47.750 --> 00:19:51.125
Parents have different ways
of showing their love, Honey.

363
00:19:51.208 --> 00:19:53.666
That's what my dad said.

364
00:19:55.958 --> 00:19:58.958
[Irfan] But, your mother loves you.

365
00:19:59.708 --> 00:20:04.500
That's why he wants to
make sure I'm fighting for you.

366
00:20:08.958 --> 00:20:11.625
-Peace be upon you, Madam.
-Peace be upon you.

367
00:20:11.708 --> 00:20:13.583
If I may, I have something
I would like to say…

368
00:20:16.833 --> 00:20:18.083
I beg you, Madam.

369
00:20:23.583 --> 00:20:26.791
I'm serious about Norma, I love her.

370
00:20:26.875 --> 00:20:29.083
I promise you,
I'll bring happiness to Norma,

371
00:20:29.166 --> 00:20:32.291
take care of her, and never hurt her.

372
00:20:36.166 --> 00:20:38.125
Who allowed you to come inside?

373
00:20:41.208 --> 00:20:42.375
Norma, Madam.

374
00:20:42.458 --> 00:20:45.208
-If that's the case, get out now.
-Mom!

375
00:20:46.291 --> 00:20:47.458
This is my house.

376
00:20:48.833 --> 00:20:49.833
[Norma] Mom!

377
00:20:53.125 --> 00:20:54.875
I don’t wanna talk about it.

378
00:20:55.625 --> 00:20:57.083
Who do you wanna choose, me or him?

379
00:20:57.166 --> 00:21:00.083
Why do I have to choose, Mom?

380
00:21:02.208 --> 00:21:04.208
I love you!

381
00:21:05.916 --> 00:21:08.375
But I also want to be serious with him.

382
00:21:09.125 --> 00:21:10.041
I don’t like him!

383
00:21:12.458 --> 00:21:16.000
Do you dislike him, or do you dislike
that I'm serious about him?

384
00:21:16.083 --> 00:21:18.458
[Mom] Remember what
Ummi taught us yesterday?

385
00:21:18.541 --> 00:21:20.541
"Mother, mother, mother" [huffing]

386
00:21:20.625 --> 00:21:23.250
If your mother says no, it means no!

387
00:21:25.958 --> 00:21:27.916
But she also told me,

388
00:21:29.166 --> 00:21:32.541
when the Prophet forbids something,
there must be a reason…

389
00:21:34.000 --> 00:21:36.166
…I don't understand yours.

390
00:21:38.958 --> 00:21:40.708
You don’t need to!

391
00:21:46.500 --> 00:21:47.958
[Irfan] So, you want to break up?

392
00:21:48.041 --> 00:21:50.125
[Norma] I don't want to be a bad daughter.

393
00:21:52.791 --> 00:21:54.833
Do you still want to fight for us?

394
00:21:57.833 --> 00:22:00.166
Shall we go to Jakarta to see your dad?

395
00:22:00.916 --> 00:22:02.875
It's your dad who will be
our marriage guardian.

396
00:22:06.125 --> 00:22:08.250
[train horn blaring]

397
00:22:08.333 --> 00:22:09.500
Peace be upon you.

398
00:22:09.583 --> 00:22:10.583
[Norma] Dad…

399
00:22:11.333 --> 00:22:13.250
[Dad] Peace be upon you.

400
00:22:13.833 --> 00:22:16.291
When I was at the square…

401
00:22:16.375 --> 00:22:21.208
I was worried that you just
wanna have fun with her.

402
00:22:21.291 --> 00:22:25.083
But you intend to bring Norma here.

403
00:22:25.166 --> 00:22:28.083
I believe you’re serious about her.

404
00:22:28.166 --> 00:22:31.833
Also, I’m quite sure…

405
00:22:31.916 --> 00:22:35.250
…many of her male friends
couldn't stand her mother.

406
00:22:35.333 --> 00:22:37.625
I am truly in love with Norma, Sir.

407
00:22:42.958 --> 00:22:45.958
I love Irfan too, Dad.

408
00:22:46.625 --> 00:22:48.500
If God wills, I want us to be serious.

409
00:22:51.000 --> 00:22:54.583
Yeah, it’s a relief for me,
if you have the same feeling.

410
00:22:54.666 --> 00:22:57.750
If you want to get married soon…

411
00:22:57.833 --> 00:23:00.000
…then go ahead.

412
00:23:00.083 --> 00:23:04.166
You two take care of the wedding,
I'll take care of Mom.

413
00:23:04.250 --> 00:23:08.750
[happy music]

414
00:23:11.375 --> 00:23:13.208
Thank God!

415
00:23:13.291 --> 00:23:14.708
You've already agreed?

416
00:23:15.708 --> 00:23:17.375
You want to go against me?

417
00:23:17.458 --> 00:23:21.375
[Dad] Look, I don't want to fight, okay!

418
00:23:21.458 --> 00:23:22.833
Please stop!

419
00:23:23.416 --> 00:23:25.916
Norma is a grown-up now.

420
00:23:26.708 --> 00:23:30.208
If they are meant to be,
it is not good to obstruct them.

421
00:23:30.291 --> 00:23:32.708
How do you know they're meant to be?

422
00:23:32.791 --> 00:23:34.041
[deep breath]

423
00:23:34.125 --> 00:23:38.458
-Will this kind of thing last a lifetime?
-Well, who knows if it can.

424
00:23:39.208 --> 00:23:41.875
But if they love each other,
why should we stop them?

425
00:23:41.958 --> 00:23:43.791
Why don’t we support them?

426
00:23:43.875 --> 00:23:47.916
We can have a good marriage
even without love.

427
00:23:48.000 --> 00:23:49.541
[Dad] What’s ‘good’ here, you think?

428
00:23:49.625 --> 00:23:52.500
You say a marriage like this is fine.

429
00:23:53.750 --> 00:23:56.791
You're objecting
because you care about her?

430
00:23:57.458 --> 00:24:00.541
Or because you don’t
want to see her happy?

431
00:24:02.625 --> 00:24:07.000
Happy? What does she know about 'happy'?

432
00:24:09.666 --> 00:24:11.875
She knows better than you.

433
00:24:11.958 --> 00:24:13.541
[train rumbling by]

434
00:24:15.333 --> 00:24:17.333
I am not agreeing to this! [choking sound]

435
00:24:18.000 --> 00:24:20.291
[Dad] Okay, fine!

436
00:24:21.041 --> 00:24:24.875
I will marry them off,

437
00:24:24.958 --> 00:24:28.666
with or without your consent!

438
00:24:40.000 --> 00:24:45.458
[pensive music]

439
00:24:50.583 --> 00:24:53.541
[Dad] Irfan Wardhana,
son of Agus Wardana,

440
00:24:53.625 --> 00:24:56.083
I marry you to my daughter…

441
00:24:56.166 --> 00:24:59.166
Norma Risma, daughter of Abdul Mahmud

442
00:24:59.250 --> 00:25:04.416
with a dowry of Rp 1.312.2023,

443
00:25:04.500 --> 00:25:07.625
and ten grams of gold paid in cash.

444
00:25:07.708 --> 00:25:11.250
I accept the marriage to
Norma Risma, daughter of Abdul Mahmud.

445
00:25:11.333 --> 00:25:13.166
With the aforementioned
dowry paid in cash.

446
00:25:13.750 --> 00:25:14.833
It's official!

447
00:25:16.333 --> 00:25:18.250
[person in audience] Our Lord, give us

448
00:25:18.333 --> 00:25:21.375
good in this world, and in the Hereafter,

449
00:25:21.458 --> 00:25:23.375
and protect us from the torment of Fire.

450
00:25:24.166 --> 00:25:29.291
Please take care of Norma
as best as you can.

451
00:25:29.375 --> 00:25:32.250
[sobbing] May you always be happy.

452
00:25:32.333 --> 00:25:37.791
[thoughtfull music]

453
00:25:41.000 --> 00:25:42.041
[Norma] Mom…

454
00:25:42.125 --> 00:25:43.291
[sobbing]

455
00:25:44.083 --> 00:25:45.250
[sobbing] Dad…

456
00:25:45.750 --> 00:25:49.916
Thank you for raising me with love.

457
00:25:50.875 --> 00:25:52.708
[Norma] Please give us a blessing, Dad.

458
00:25:52.791 --> 00:25:54.541
[quiet sobbing]

459
00:25:54.625 --> 00:25:58.041
May you always be happy, Dear.

460
00:26:03.625 --> 00:26:08.916
[quiet background music]

461
00:26:22.416 --> 00:26:23.791
Mom…

462
00:26:24.958 --> 00:26:28.125
You’re the most
important person in my life.

463
00:26:28.208 --> 00:26:30.500
I love you, Mom.

464
00:26:35.583 --> 00:26:37.125
Please give us your blessings, Mom.

465
00:26:39.416 --> 00:26:41.041
You have hurt me…

466
00:26:45.291 --> 00:26:47.041
…but I already forgive you.

467
00:26:48.208 --> 00:26:50.125
[Mom] I hope your choice
is the right one for you, Dear.

468
00:26:58.083 --> 00:27:02.291
[swelling music]

469
00:27:02.375 --> 00:27:03.291
[crowd murmering]

470
00:27:13.250 --> 00:27:14.166
[camera clicking]

471
00:27:16.625 --> 00:27:17.875
[cameraman] 1,2,3!

472
00:27:17.958 --> 00:27:19.250
[loud camera flash]

473
00:27:24.666 --> 00:27:26.083
Hi, my dear wife!

474
00:27:29.333 --> 00:27:31.291
Hi, my husband!

475
00:27:36.500 --> 00:27:41.625
It's funny, just brushing my teeth
makes me so happy!

476
00:27:44.916 --> 00:27:47.958
[both giggling]

477
00:27:53.041 --> 00:27:54.416
Saving for Umrah.

478
00:27:55.708 --> 00:27:57.333
I want to ask my mom.

479
00:27:57.416 --> 00:28:01.583
[soft music]

480
00:28:01.666 --> 00:28:04.000
You also display the lollipop
I gave you to you, Honey?

481
00:28:05.625 --> 00:28:07.250
[giggling]

482
00:28:08.541 --> 00:28:09.500
Yes!

483
00:28:11.166 --> 00:28:14.166
I can't believe we actually got married.

484
00:28:16.125 --> 00:28:18.291
Thank God,
Mom has finally given us her blessing.

485
00:28:19.458 --> 00:28:20.458
[door slamiing]

486
00:28:25.958 --> 00:28:28.583
Shouldn't we move to
a rented house, Honey?

487
00:28:28.666 --> 00:28:30.500
So you can be comfortable too.

488
00:28:31.083 --> 00:28:32.250
[mild sigh]

489
00:28:35.083 --> 00:28:36.750
I don't think it's necessary, Honey.

490
00:28:36.833 --> 00:28:39.416
I'm afraid your mom
might dislike me even more.

491
00:28:40.958 --> 00:28:44.708
Besides, I promised your father
to take care of her.

492
00:28:46.625 --> 00:28:48.625
Your mom is also my mom too.

493
00:28:48.708 --> 00:28:52.833
[soft music]

494
00:29:01.458 --> 00:29:03.083
[Irfan] Trust me.

495
00:29:04.708 --> 00:29:09.291
If God is willing,
slowly she can accept me.

496
00:29:13.125 --> 00:29:14.875
Let’s take care of Mom together.

497
00:29:22.666 --> 00:29:24.125
[giggling]

498
00:29:33.666 --> 00:29:35.291
Ah, I'm shy!

499
00:29:41.583 --> 00:29:43.250
[giggling]

500
00:29:43.916 --> 00:29:46.458
-Honey, I’m shy!
-[laughing]

501
00:29:53.166 --> 00:29:55.625
[romantic music]

502
00:30:11.083 --> 00:30:14.000
-[quiet breathing]
-[quiet breathing]

503
00:30:16.125 --> 00:30:17.750
[giggling]

504
00:30:21.625 --> 00:30:26.000
[deep breathing and sobbing]

505
00:30:34.291 --> 00:30:35.375
[crying]

506
00:30:39.666 --> 00:30:41.916
Sorry Honey, I’m leaving early.

507
00:30:42.000 --> 00:30:43.833
Shift start times keep changing.

508
00:30:56.916 --> 00:30:58.750
Aw, stop!

509
00:31:05.291 --> 00:31:06.125
[kissing sound]

510
00:31:06.208 --> 00:31:07.625
I'm leaving now, Honey.

511
00:31:09.583 --> 00:31:10.791
[Norma] Take care, Honey!

512
00:31:10.875 --> 00:31:17.125
[dramatic music building]

513
00:31:22.291 --> 00:31:23.791
Just go, or you'll be late!

514
00:31:28.625 --> 00:31:30.916
Be careful, and bring the things
that are upstairs too.

515
00:31:31.000 --> 00:31:31.875
Yes, Mr Irfan!

516
00:31:33.416 --> 00:31:34.541
-Andri.
-[Andri] Yes, Sir?

517
00:31:34.625 --> 00:31:36.500
-Did the items arrive?
-Yes, Boss.

518
00:31:36.583 --> 00:31:38.666
Everyone, let's gather in the middle!

519
00:31:38.750 --> 00:31:43.625
So we're going to change shifts, please
check and make sure all is in order!

520
00:31:43.708 --> 00:31:46.916
Remember our motto, Honesty and Trust!

521
00:31:47.000 --> 00:31:50.416
Ladies and gentlemen,
let's get back to work.

522
00:31:51.125 --> 00:31:53.708
Alright, back to work, let's go, let's go!

523
00:31:55.583 --> 00:31:57.541
Here we are, the newlyweds!

524
00:31:58.791 --> 00:32:01.083
Irfan, you look much more buff!
Are you working out these days?

525
00:32:01.958 --> 00:32:06.333
-Don't joke like that.
-Hey, I'm serious. You look buff!

526
00:32:06.416 --> 00:32:07.375
[female giggle]

527
00:32:08.291 --> 00:32:11.291
So Irfan, who's better, me or her?

528
00:32:14.333 --> 00:32:16.833
-Answer my question!
-Can I have the weekly report now?

529
00:32:16.916 --> 00:32:20.250
Yes, I'll give it to you later.
But, is she better or am I?

530
00:32:20.333 --> 00:32:21.541
Peace be upon you!

531
00:32:22.583 --> 00:32:25.416
Peace be upon you.
Honey, what time did you arrive?

532
00:32:25.958 --> 00:32:27.583
We had an appointment at 3 PM.

533
00:32:28.708 --> 00:32:29.916
Oh right!

534
00:32:31.375 --> 00:32:32.375
[embarrased umm]

535
00:32:32.458 --> 00:32:34.541
This is Etni, my team member.

536
00:32:34.625 --> 00:32:37.541
-Hi, I’m Etni
-Norma.

537
00:32:37.625 --> 00:32:40.791
Congrats on your wedding,
sorry I couldn't make it.

538
00:32:40.875 --> 00:32:43.000
How thoughtful of Irfan
not to invite his ex.

539
00:32:45.458 --> 00:32:47.291
I'm going over there now, okay?

540
00:32:48.166 --> 00:32:51.291
[pensive music]

541
00:32:51.375 --> 00:32:52.708
Are we going now?

542
00:32:53.500 --> 00:32:54.708
Let’s go!

543
00:32:54.791 --> 00:32:56.958
Do you want to come inside?
I'll prepare for a bit.

544
00:32:57.041 --> 00:32:58.125
I’ll stay here.

545
00:32:58.208 --> 00:32:59.875
Alright, please wait for me.

546
00:33:11.541 --> 00:33:13.958
Honey, how long has it been
since you broke up with Etni?

547
00:33:18.125 --> 00:33:21.000
Hmm, let me see…

548
00:33:22.458 --> 00:33:24.208
I don't remember, Honey,
it's been a long time.

549
00:33:28.541 --> 00:33:29.875
Well, okay.

550
00:33:32.583 --> 00:33:36.833
Be careful, okay? You're in the
same job with her.

551
00:33:36.916 --> 00:33:40.250
Since she is your ex,
there must have been feelings left.

552
00:33:40.333 --> 00:33:43.083
It's nice to be noticed by my wife!

553
00:33:45.291 --> 00:33:48.041
Honey, have you responded to Rika's offer?

554
00:33:49.208 --> 00:33:51.666
Rika keeps asking me.

555
00:33:51.750 --> 00:33:54.916
But Mom hasn't allowed it,
and I don't know why.

556
00:33:55.000 --> 00:33:57.750
I wonder why.
The salary is pretty good, right?

557
00:33:57.833 --> 00:34:04.000
I think Mom is worried that no one
will help her sell chicken noodles.

558
00:34:04.083 --> 00:34:07.666
I'm the one who usually helps her
after returning from study group.

559
00:34:07.750 --> 00:34:13.208
If I teach at the school,
I won't get home until four or five.

560
00:34:15.083 --> 00:34:16.000
[deep sigh]

561
00:34:19.666 --> 00:34:21.166
These chicken noodles are tasty, right?

562
00:34:21.750 --> 00:34:25.833
But for me, no one can surpass
Mom's chicken noodles!

563
00:34:26.416 --> 00:34:31.458
Her chicken noodles are
small, sweet, and savory.

564
00:34:32.166 --> 00:34:33.333
I agree, Honey.

565
00:34:35.041 --> 00:34:39.166
Honey, how about we make
a chicken noodle stall for Mom?

566
00:34:39.833 --> 00:34:43.375
The capital could come
from my Umrah savings.

567
00:34:43.458 --> 00:34:46.833
When I work with Rika,
I will save it again.

568
00:34:47.666 --> 00:34:49.833
-What do you think?
-That’s great, Honey.

569
00:34:57.166 --> 00:35:00.000
Try it, Mom, trust me.

570
00:35:00.083 --> 00:35:01.791
Your noodles are still the best!

571
00:35:01.875 --> 00:35:04.583
[slurping]

572
00:35:06.041 --> 00:35:10.333
Am I right? It’s still better from you.

573
00:35:11.458 --> 00:35:15.333
If it's this crowded, imagine how busy
it would be if you were selling.

574
00:35:18.458 --> 00:35:22.833
Mom, me and Irfan had an idea…

575
00:35:24.458 --> 00:35:28.375
…what if we open
a chicken noodle stall for you?

576
00:35:28.458 --> 00:35:29.958
It will surely be popular!

577
00:35:32.791 --> 00:35:35.791
-Where will we get the capital?
-From me.

578
00:35:35.875 --> 00:35:37.375
I have savings.

579
00:35:41.708 --> 00:35:43.083
Come on, Mom!

580
00:35:43.166 --> 00:35:47.166
I really want everyone to try
the chicken noodles you make.

581
00:35:47.250 --> 00:35:52.416
We'll name it "MIE RINA".

582
00:35:52.500 --> 00:35:57.875
[light happy music]

583
00:35:57.958 --> 00:36:01.166
Irfan is good at painting. Perfect!

584
00:36:01.250 --> 00:36:02.125
Hi.

585
00:36:02.666 --> 00:36:06.916
Irfan, Auntie asked me to help you.
What can I do for you?

586
00:36:07.000 --> 00:36:09.083
Just clean up the inside first?

587
00:36:09.166 --> 00:36:11.666
-Is it too much?
-No, it's fine!

588
00:36:11.750 --> 00:36:14.541
-You guys, please come and join me!
-Okay.

589
00:36:14.625 --> 00:36:16.041
-Thank you!
-It's fine.

590
00:36:16.125 --> 00:36:20.583
[upbeat music]

591
00:36:22.958 --> 00:36:23.833
[mixer noise]

592
00:36:33.166 --> 00:36:35.041
-[Irfan] Peace be upon you, Honey.
-Peace be upon you.

593
00:36:35.125 --> 00:36:36.041
Where’s Mom?

594
00:36:37.125 --> 00:36:38.083
In the kitchen.

595
00:36:43.333 --> 00:36:44.333
[sniffing]

596
00:36:47.041 --> 00:36:47.875
MENU

597
00:36:47.958 --> 00:36:48.833
[helper friend] Boss!

598
00:36:48.916 --> 00:36:50.291
Hey!

599
00:36:50.375 --> 00:36:51.791
Hello Boss!

600
00:36:52.583 --> 00:36:54.708
-Is everything done?
-Yeah, it’s finished, Sir.

601
00:36:54.791 --> 00:36:56.125
-This is the last one.
-Hey!

602
00:36:56.208 --> 00:36:57.333
Hey, help me!

603
00:36:59.625 --> 00:37:00.500
Any others, Honey?

604
00:37:04.708 --> 00:37:06.083
If it's like this, is it tilted?

605
00:37:08.041 --> 00:37:10.750
Honey, I just asked
but you stared blankly.

606
00:37:10.833 --> 00:37:12.875
Is it crooked or not, huh?

607
00:37:13.625 --> 00:37:15.583
[Irfan] In the name of Allah!

608
00:37:16.083 --> 00:37:19.125
[applause]

609
00:37:19.208 --> 00:37:20.166
It's great.

610
00:37:20.750 --> 00:37:22.416
-Good job, Boss!
-[Auntie] Congrats Rina!

611
00:37:22.500 --> 00:37:26.250
I'm really happy for you!

612
00:37:26.333 --> 00:37:27.208
[happy chuckles]

613
00:37:29.083 --> 00:37:30.541
MIERINA CHICKEN NOODLES
MEATBALLS, DUMPLINGS, MUSHROOMS

614
00:37:30.625 --> 00:37:32.458
[Irfan] Thanks, everyone!

615
00:37:32.541 --> 00:37:34.666
-Thank you.
-Yeah.

616
00:37:36.041 --> 00:37:41.666
[happy music builds]

617
00:37:47.291 --> 00:37:50.208
-Thank you.
-Sure. Good luck…

618
00:37:51.083 --> 00:37:52.916
[Norma] Please enjoy!

619
00:37:53.000 --> 00:37:55.375
-Excuse me, Sir and Madam.
-Thank you.

620
00:37:55.458 --> 00:37:58.666
-Enjoy your meal!
-Please enjoy your meal!

621
00:37:59.875 --> 00:38:02.333
-Mom?
-Yes, Dear?

622
00:38:02.416 --> 00:38:04.083
Peace be upon you. Thanks for coming.

623
00:38:04.166 --> 00:38:06.166
Peace be upon you. It’s my pleasure, Dear.

624
00:38:06.250 --> 00:38:07.250
Mom!

625
00:38:08.166 --> 00:38:10.750
[Irfan's mom] Peace be upon you, in-law!

626
00:38:10.833 --> 00:38:14.541
-Congratulations on the opening.
-Thank you.

627
00:38:15.125 --> 00:38:16.416
[excited sigh]

628
00:38:16.500 --> 00:38:19.500
It's so crowded,
I hope it sells really well!

629
00:38:19.583 --> 00:38:23.958
Please have a seat.
I will bring it to you later.

630
00:38:24.041 --> 00:38:25.666
Could I have chicken noodles to-go?

631
00:38:25.750 --> 00:38:29.916
Mira, Irfan's sister,
just arrived from Jakarta.

632
00:38:30.000 --> 00:38:32.625
-[Irfan's mom] Maybe next time?
-Don't you want to eat here, Mom?

633
00:38:32.708 --> 00:38:36.583
Your sister hasn't eaten yet!
What if her gastritis acts up?

634
00:38:36.666 --> 00:38:37.750
[dishes rattling in background]

635
00:38:37.833 --> 00:38:40.500
-It's okay, Mom.
-Mom!

636
00:38:43.875 --> 00:38:47.541
-When it's my day off, I help my mom.
-[Irfan's mom] Aw, what a good daughter!

637
00:38:47.625 --> 00:38:52.458
[thoughtfull music]

638
00:38:53.875 --> 00:38:54.791
[coughing off screen]

639
00:38:55.708 --> 00:38:58.916
-Tomorrow morning I have a meeting.
-[murmer of assent]

640
00:38:59.000 --> 00:39:00.375
Are you going to be late?

641
00:39:01.250 --> 00:39:04.458
Fine, I'll take you there.
I'm almost done.

642
00:39:04.541 --> 00:39:06.333
Honey, you can go inside first.

643
00:39:09.333 --> 00:39:13.333
Mom, can I go home now?

644
00:39:13.416 --> 00:39:16.166
I have to prepare for my meeting tomorrow.

645
00:39:16.750 --> 00:39:18.208
Yeah, it's fine.

646
00:39:25.000 --> 00:39:27.083
-Auntie, I'm going home first.
-Yes, be careful!

647
00:39:27.166 --> 00:39:29.791
-Peace be upon you.
-[Auntie] Peace be upon you.

648
00:39:29.875 --> 00:39:31.208
Can you wait for me on the bike, Honey?

649
00:39:35.666 --> 00:39:36.500
[door closing]

650
00:39:37.833 --> 00:39:38.833
Auntie.

651
00:39:40.000 --> 00:39:40.958
[kissing noise]

652
00:39:41.833 --> 00:39:45.750
Mom, I'll take Norma home, okay?
I'll come back to pick you up later.

653
00:39:46.333 --> 00:39:48.916
Oh, no need.
I'll go home with Auntie later.

654
00:39:49.000 --> 00:39:53.000
Don't worry, just come with me.
It'll be quick.

655
00:39:57.500 --> 00:40:00.875
[thoughtfull faint music]

656
00:40:00.958 --> 00:40:04.583
Your hands smell so good, Mom, even
after selling chicken noodles all day.

657
00:40:04.666 --> 00:40:08.750
No, it's definitely just
the scallion smell!

658
00:40:08.833 --> 00:40:12.625
It's really smells good, Auntie.
Are you sure it's scallions?

659
00:40:14.125 --> 00:40:16.958
-Peace be upon you.
-[Auntie] Peace be upon you.

660
00:40:17.041 --> 00:40:19.333
[Irfan] Honey, please wait for me!

661
00:40:24.791 --> 00:40:26.375
[dishes rattling]

662
00:40:39.500 --> 00:40:41.000
[sniffing]

663
00:40:43.875 --> 00:40:49.958
[thoughtfull faint music]

664
00:40:53.041 --> 00:40:54.208
[Irfan] Please forgive me, God!

665
00:40:54.916 --> 00:40:56.041
Gosh!

666
00:40:57.833 --> 00:40:59.125
are you okay, Mom?

667
00:40:59.208 --> 00:41:01.041
Sorry, Mom, I didn't see the hole!

668
00:41:01.791 --> 00:41:02.625
O Allah.

669
00:41:06.208 --> 00:41:07.625
Hold on tight, Mom.

670
00:41:16.000 --> 00:41:21.541
[pensive music]

671
00:42:01.666 --> 00:42:07.625
[dramatic music building]

672
00:42:16.500 --> 00:42:20.125
-Mom, let me help you.
-No need!

673
00:42:20.208 --> 00:42:24.041
It's okay, Mom. You've been working
all morning, you must be tired!

674
00:42:29.208 --> 00:42:31.750
Oh, you're wearing my lipstick, Mom?

675
00:42:32.333 --> 00:42:36.375
You look great, beautiful and glowing!

676
00:42:51.458 --> 00:42:52.541
I'm hungry.

677
00:42:52.625 --> 00:42:54.500
Yeah, me too.

678
00:42:54.583 --> 00:42:59.083
Wow, the boss is so generous.

679
00:42:59.166 --> 00:43:01.500
[Irfan's staff]
We got treated to a meal and got served!

680
00:43:01.583 --> 00:43:02.666
Thanks, Boss!

681
00:43:02.750 --> 00:43:04.583
-Thank you, Boss.
-Sit somewhere else.

682
00:43:04.666 --> 00:43:07.791
You just sit there,
so Irfan can be next to me!

683
00:43:14.250 --> 00:43:16.125
-Come here. Sit here.
-Boss.

684
00:43:18.208 --> 00:43:19.333
Here, sit over here.

685
00:43:20.625 --> 00:43:23.375
It's been a while since we sat
next to each other, right?

686
00:43:26.291 --> 00:43:27.166
Etni.

687
00:43:28.416 --> 00:43:32.125
[Fajri] Come on, don't flirt with
him! He's a married man, have some shame!

688
00:43:32.208 --> 00:43:36.125
Just let me, Fajri.
He's still willing to be flirted with!

689
00:43:36.208 --> 00:43:37.916
He just pretends to be aloof!

690
00:43:38.000 --> 00:43:40.541
Right? When there were just the two of us?

691
00:43:40.625 --> 00:43:43.750
-[Fajri] Stop and enjoy it!
-Yes, enjoy!

692
00:43:45.291 --> 00:43:46.291
Is it good?

693
00:43:46.916 --> 00:43:48.333
-Wow, it’s so good!
-Delicious!

694
00:43:53.083 --> 00:43:54.083
[quiet sob]

695
00:43:59.750 --> 00:44:05.500
[soft suspensful music]

696
00:44:05.583 --> 00:44:07.416
[light snoring]

697
00:44:20.500 --> 00:44:21.875
[keypad tapping]

698
00:44:27.208 --> 00:44:28.625
[Irfan] What were you doing, Honey?

699
00:44:34.583 --> 00:44:35.791
Nothing!

700
00:44:38.500 --> 00:44:40.041
Did you check my phone?

701
00:44:41.375 --> 00:44:42.541
No!

702
00:44:44.458 --> 00:44:45.791
Don't lie, it's a sin!

703
00:44:58.625 --> 00:44:59.583
Mom said…

704
00:45:01.750 --> 00:45:04.416
…you were being flirted with by Etni.

705
00:45:05.083 --> 00:45:06.958
What, when?

706
00:45:08.083 --> 00:45:10.416
When you were at the stall.

707
00:45:11.375 --> 00:45:15.541
Oh my gosh, Honey!

708
00:45:16.250 --> 00:45:20.875
Anyway, Etni flirts with everyone,
not just me!

709
00:45:23.166 --> 00:45:27.125
Really? [tsk tsk] It's a sin to lie!

710
00:45:28.375 --> 00:45:32.666
I dont lie, you don't believe me?

711
00:45:32.750 --> 00:45:34.666
[short sigh]

712
00:45:35.666 --> 00:45:42.166
I'm just reminding you,
she is quite attentive to you.

713
00:45:42.250 --> 00:45:43.125
[short sigh]

714
00:45:43.875 --> 00:45:47.125
I know, let’s take a rest, okay?

715
00:45:49.708 --> 00:45:50.708
[coughing]

716
00:46:03.750 --> 00:46:04.833
[light sigh]

717
00:46:07.041 --> 00:46:08.000
[shallow breathing]

718
00:46:09.083 --> 00:46:15.833
[soft thoughtful music]

719
00:46:20.125 --> 00:46:21.083
[shallow breath]

720
00:46:21.583 --> 00:46:25.791
[thunder]

721
00:46:27.916 --> 00:46:28.750
Mom?

722
00:46:30.083 --> 00:46:31.125
Yes, Irfan?

723
00:46:32.250 --> 00:46:35.250
Norma is already asleep, but I can't.

724
00:46:36.458 --> 00:46:37.666
Can I watch TV with you?

725
00:46:40.291 --> 00:46:41.125
[faint TV noise]

726
00:46:46.625 --> 00:46:50.458
[Irfan] Mom, about this afternoon,

727
00:46:50.541 --> 00:46:53.583
I swear there's
nothing between me and her.

728
00:46:54.625 --> 00:46:55.666
Is that so?

729
00:46:58.208 --> 00:47:02.583
Mom, I truly want to show you
that I'm a good son

730
00:47:02.666 --> 00:47:04.000
and not the type to cause trouble.

731
00:47:05.416 --> 00:47:07.333
I would never hurt you, Mom.

732
00:47:07.416 --> 00:47:10.791
[faint TV noise]

733
00:47:10.875 --> 00:47:11.958
Okay.

734
00:47:13.958 --> 00:47:15.458
Prove it.

735
00:47:17.166 --> 00:47:18.250
I’ll go first.

736
00:47:26.958 --> 00:47:28.916
-Peace be upon you.
-Peace be upon you.

737
00:47:29.000 --> 00:47:33.333
-How's that, Miss? Not too late, right?
-Very impressive, Mr. Fajri.

738
00:47:33.416 --> 00:47:36.208
-May I help you?
-No need!

739
00:47:36.291 --> 00:47:38.541
-[happy chuckle]
-Miss, let me do it.

740
00:47:41.541 --> 00:47:44.375
Should I help you take this inside?

741
00:47:44.458 --> 00:47:48.791
Mr. Unim is coming here,
he'll take care of it.

742
00:47:49.791 --> 00:47:51.916
-I'll take my leave, Miss.
-Wait, Sir!

743
00:47:52.000 --> 00:47:53.166
-[umm]
-[umm]

744
00:47:54.208 --> 00:47:56.500
If it's about the fare, I have money.

745
00:47:56.583 --> 00:48:02.125
No, I'm confused about who to ask.

746
00:48:02.916 --> 00:48:04.916
It's perfect timing you’re here.

747
00:48:05.708 --> 00:48:07.208
-Why?
-[umm]

748
00:48:07.708 --> 00:48:11.125
How does Irfan

749
00:48:11.208 --> 00:48:16.666
behave around Etni in the office?

750
00:48:16.750 --> 00:48:19.708
[scared chuckle]

751
00:48:19.791 --> 00:48:24.416
It's the same as… everyone else.

752
00:48:24.500 --> 00:48:29.125
Who started working there first,
Irfan or Etni?

753
00:48:31.166 --> 00:48:32.791
Irfan!

754
00:48:33.625 --> 00:48:34.583
Yes.

755
00:48:36.541 --> 00:48:40.000
So, Etni was recruited by Mr. Irfan?

756
00:48:41.125 --> 00:48:43.208
Yes, Miss.

757
00:48:43.291 --> 00:48:45.916
Okay then, thank you, Sir.

758
00:48:46.541 --> 00:48:47.541
Umm.

759
00:48:48.208 --> 00:48:52.375
Sorry, please don't tell Irfan about this.

760
00:48:52.458 --> 00:48:55.666
Yes, Miss. I'll take my leave.

761
00:48:55.750 --> 00:48:57.208
[flustered breath] Gosh, excuse me.

762
00:48:57.291 --> 00:48:59.541
[van door closing]

763
00:48:59.625 --> 00:49:00.541
Excuse me.

764
00:49:01.416 --> 00:49:03.166
[Fajri] Excuse me, Miss.

765
00:49:04.250 --> 00:49:05.916
-[van horn beeps]
-Oh I'm sorry, Miss! I'm a new driver!

766
00:49:06.000 --> 00:49:07.208
-Be careful!
-Okay.

767
00:49:07.291 --> 00:49:10.375
[sounds of car engine]

768
00:49:10.458 --> 00:49:13.500
[soft pensive music]

769
00:49:30.833 --> 00:49:36.416
[pensive music building]

770
00:49:51.958 --> 00:49:53.208
[Irfan] Peace be upon you.

771
00:49:54.375 --> 00:49:57.041
Honey, why haven't you slept yet?

772
00:49:58.000 --> 00:50:00.708
I'll prepare a towel and
warm water for you, okay?

773
00:50:00.791 --> 00:50:01.875
Honey, take a shower now!

774
00:50:02.708 --> 00:50:04.125
Have you eaten yet?

775
00:50:09.333 --> 00:50:13.291
[footsteps]

776
00:50:18.416 --> 00:50:22.083
Mom, do you want to use this bathroom?

777
00:50:22.916 --> 00:50:23.958
Yes.

778
00:50:24.541 --> 00:50:25.708
After you.

779
00:50:26.916 --> 00:50:32.416
[soft suspensful music]

780
00:50:35.083 --> 00:50:36.375
[bathroom door closes]

781
00:50:39.583 --> 00:50:40.583
[soft suspensful music]

782
00:50:51.916 --> 00:50:53.125
[bedroom door closes]

783
00:50:53.208 --> 00:50:54.083
Honey…

784
00:50:54.166 --> 00:50:56.541
[shuffling]

785
00:50:56.625 --> 00:50:58.208
Can you explain this to me?

786
00:50:59.416 --> 00:51:02.791
See? I didn't reply to anything.
That's just how she is.

787
00:51:02.875 --> 00:51:06.166
-She doesn't just send it to me.
-But you already have a wife!

788
00:51:06.250 --> 00:51:09.791
Don't ignore chats like this,
you have to be firmer!

789
00:51:09.875 --> 00:51:12.833
[light sigh] Can
we not talk about that? I'm tired.

790
00:51:12.916 --> 00:51:15.833
-If we don't discuss it now, then when?
-[loudly] I'm tired!

791
00:51:17.250 --> 00:51:19.458
You should have asked me why I'm late!

792
00:51:20.166 --> 00:51:23.666
My bike broke down, I was soaked
from pushing it in the rain!

793
00:51:25.000 --> 00:51:28.125
Tomorrow I have to leave earlier
because it needs to go to the workshop.

794
00:51:28.666 --> 00:51:31.583
Seriously? This is the question I get?

795
00:51:32.500 --> 00:51:35.500
I'm telling you, this is important to me.

796
00:51:35.583 --> 00:51:39.333
I wouldn't be like this
if you had told me everything.

797
00:51:39.416 --> 00:51:40.750
I’m not lying!

798
00:51:40.833 --> 00:51:42.833
But you didn't tell me
that Etni is your ex.

799
00:51:42.916 --> 00:51:47.583
You hired Etni. I can't deal
with this kind of secrecy.

800
00:51:47.666 --> 00:51:50.541
Who told you this? Fajri?

801
00:51:50.625 --> 00:51:53.625
If it's about recruitment,
there are many, not just Etni.

802
00:51:53.708 --> 00:51:54.833
Alright…

803
00:51:55.416 --> 00:51:58.625
If there were many people who applied,
why should you hire her instead?

804
00:52:00.458 --> 00:52:03.791
It's over, there's no point
in discussing this anymore.

805
00:52:04.708 --> 00:52:08.458
You're being childish. I'm always wrong,
and it's frustrating me!

806
00:52:11.500 --> 00:52:13.708
[door opens and shuts]

807
00:52:18.250 --> 00:52:19.208
[coughing]

808
00:52:19.916 --> 00:52:22.666
[deep sigh]

809
00:52:24.666 --> 00:52:25.916
What’s wrong with you?

810
00:52:30.083 --> 00:52:32.375
Sorry Mom, is it noisy?

811
00:52:32.958 --> 00:52:33.875
Are you sick?

812
00:52:34.958 --> 00:52:36.166
I think I have a cold.

813
00:52:40.875 --> 00:52:42.250
Drink something warm, okay?

814
00:52:46.750 --> 00:52:49.500
[sniffling]

815
00:52:52.291 --> 00:52:54.000
Drink this to feel better.

816
00:52:55.833 --> 00:52:56.916
Thank you, Mom.

817
00:53:04.458 --> 00:53:08.166
-No need, Mom. It's okay.
-Don't get sick, just drink.

818
00:53:21.375 --> 00:53:23.916
[coughing]

819
00:53:25.625 --> 00:53:27.416
Why did you sleep out here?

820
00:53:29.083 --> 00:53:30.166
Did you two have a fight?

821
00:53:31.583 --> 00:53:36.291
It's Etni, Mom,
Norma has a misunderstanding.

822
00:53:36.375 --> 00:53:39.125
I don't know how to make it any clearer.

823
00:53:40.750 --> 00:53:42.333
What did I do wrong?

824
00:53:43.583 --> 00:53:48.958
You'll have to be patient with Norma,
she's been very spoiled by her dad.

825
00:53:49.041 --> 00:53:52.583
[coughing]

826
00:53:53.875 --> 00:53:56.250
Are you going to throw up?
Should I give you a massage?

827
00:53:56.333 --> 00:53:58.083
No need, Mom.

828
00:53:58.166 --> 00:54:00.000
[deep breath]

829
00:54:00.916 --> 00:54:03.500
Or can you apply some balm, Mom?

830
00:54:03.583 --> 00:54:05.666
-Shall I call Norma?
-No need, Mom.

831
00:54:07.208 --> 00:54:08.458
No need Mom, thanks.

832
00:54:08.541 --> 00:54:11.583
[coughing]

833
00:54:14.583 --> 00:54:17.500
[coughing]

834
00:54:23.250 --> 00:54:25.625
Okay, take off you shirt.

835
00:54:42.583 --> 00:54:48.291
[soft suspenseful music]

836
00:55:14.000 --> 00:55:14.875
Done.

837
00:55:22.291 --> 00:55:24.666
That feels so good, Mom. Thank you.

838
00:55:26.166 --> 00:55:27.250
Better?

839
00:55:29.500 --> 00:55:31.291
Better after seeing you smile, Mom.

840
00:55:31.375 --> 00:55:32.291
You're beautiful!

841
00:55:37.208 --> 00:55:40.916
-I'm sorry, Mom, I mean…
-Thank you.

842
00:55:44.000 --> 00:55:46.375
No one has complimented
my beauty in a long time.

843
00:55:46.458 --> 00:55:52.208
[soft thoughtful music]

844
00:55:53.875 --> 00:55:55.125
Have you sweated yet?

845
00:55:56.416 --> 00:55:58.083
How are your feeling?

846
00:56:11.291 --> 00:56:12.125
[confused murmer]

847
00:56:12.625 --> 00:56:14.000
Sorry.

848
00:56:19.541 --> 00:56:20.625
[door opens and shuts]

849
00:56:23.250 --> 00:56:25.833
[sound of rainfall]

850
00:56:26.416 --> 00:56:28.708
Rina, I'm going home first, okay?

851
00:56:28.791 --> 00:56:31.500
Can't you wait until
the rain stops, instead?

852
00:56:31.583 --> 00:56:34.833
No, it will only get worse later.

853
00:56:34.916 --> 00:56:37.541
Besides, my bike is still in the workshop.

854
00:56:38.541 --> 00:56:41.041
-Alright, be careful, Auntie.
-[Auntie] Thanks.

855
00:56:41.125 --> 00:56:43.833
-Peace be upon you.
-Peace be upon you.

856
00:56:43.916 --> 00:56:47.583
Wow, the rain is really heavy!

857
00:56:47.666 --> 00:56:49.416
MIERINA CHICKEN NOODLES
MEATBALLS, DUMPLINGS, MUSHROOMS

858
00:56:55.458 --> 00:56:58.125
[motorcycle arriving]

859
00:57:00.125 --> 00:57:03.583
[thunder]

860
00:57:06.625 --> 00:57:09.500
-[Irfan] Peace be upon you.
-Peace be upon you.

861
00:57:10.041 --> 00:57:13.375
Why are you here in the rain?
The noodles are all gone.

862
00:57:37.250 --> 00:57:40.541
[cell phone ringing]

863
00:57:46.166 --> 00:57:50.125
Why not go home?
Norma's going to look for you.

864
00:57:51.458 --> 00:57:53.083
She's been waiting at home all day.

865
00:57:53.916 --> 00:57:58.041
I'd rather wait a bit, Mom,
it's not comfortable at home.

866
00:58:00.875 --> 00:58:04.541
Mom, don't you trust me?
I've been trying to change.

867
00:58:06.375 --> 00:58:08.958
For Norma, for you.

868
00:58:09.833 --> 00:58:11.541
But if even you,
who don't believe me, Mom…

869
00:58:14.625 --> 00:58:16.458
I trust you.

870
00:58:16.958 --> 00:58:23.291
[light music]

871
00:58:23.875 --> 00:58:28.958
All that matters to me now
is that you believe in me, Mom.

872
00:58:30.250 --> 00:58:33.583
Because it's harder to convince you,
rather than Norma.

873
00:59:03.625 --> 00:59:05.375
I really like someone like you, Mom.

874
00:59:07.291 --> 00:59:10.208
You are a strong and assertive woman.

875
00:59:10.958 --> 00:59:13.166
Not fickle at all.

876
00:59:13.250 --> 00:59:16.208
I don't understand why
Dad is missing out on you.

877
00:59:34.125 --> 00:59:39.708
[light music]

878
00:59:42.666 --> 00:59:45.041
You look so beautiful with red lipstick.

879
00:59:46.833 --> 00:59:48.333
[deep sigh]

880
01:00:11.166 --> 01:00:16.833
[dramatic music builds]

881
01:00:29.500 --> 01:00:34.833
[music swells]

882
01:00:34.916 --> 01:00:37.291
[startled breath]

883
01:00:37.375 --> 01:00:39.375
S-Sorry, Mom.

884
01:00:40.500 --> 01:00:43.666
I can’t lie… you feel it too, right?

885
01:00:46.000 --> 01:00:46.958
Go!

886
01:00:49.833 --> 01:00:51.000
Leave now!

887
01:00:52.041 --> 01:00:55.291
[breathing fast]

888
01:00:59.250 --> 01:01:03.000
[falling rain]

889
01:01:17.875 --> 01:01:18.833
[door opens]

890
01:01:19.458 --> 01:01:22.833
-[Irfan] Peace be upon you.
-Peace be upon you.

891
01:01:24.375 --> 01:01:26.791
-Would you like some tea?
-Please, have a seat.

892
01:01:26.875 --> 01:01:29.083
[deep sigh]

893
01:01:32.166 --> 01:01:36.083
I was wrong,
I should have told you about Etni.

894
01:01:36.666 --> 01:01:39.083
[sobbing] But I had
absolutely no bad intentions.

895
01:01:40.458 --> 01:01:44.333
I don't want you to get hurt
by needless worries.

896
01:01:44.916 --> 01:01:47.583
Now, I also want to admit… [deep sigh]

897
01:01:47.666 --> 01:01:51.166
Etni wasn't my only ex,
I had a few others.

898
01:01:51.666 --> 01:01:54.250
But that's the past. Just the past.

899
01:01:56.000 --> 01:02:00.000
I married you because
I genuinely want to change.

900
01:02:00.083 --> 01:02:02.166
I want to be the right person for you.

901
01:02:05.583 --> 01:02:09.125
I can't change the past, but can we…

902
01:02:09.958 --> 01:02:11.333
[short breath]

903
01:02:11.416 --> 01:02:15.125
…please start over and
have no more distrust?

904
01:02:20.541 --> 01:02:21.708
It's okay…

905
01:02:23.125 --> 01:02:24.916
[sniffle]

906
01:02:26.250 --> 01:02:27.791
Please forgive me too.

907
01:02:35.625 --> 01:02:38.125
You're the only one
I have in my heart now.

908
01:03:00.791 --> 01:03:03.333
[sobbing]

909
01:03:04.250 --> 01:03:05.416
Honey!

910
01:03:08.541 --> 01:03:09.583
Honey!

911
01:03:14.500 --> 01:03:17.333
Honey, it's okay!

912
01:03:17.416 --> 01:03:19.583
Shush…

913
01:03:19.666 --> 01:03:20.750
[sobbing]

914
01:03:20.833 --> 01:03:23.416
Please forgive me, Honey!

915
01:03:23.500 --> 01:03:26.750
It's okay. Seek forgiveness from God.

916
01:03:26.833 --> 01:03:28.208
[sobbing]

917
01:03:28.291 --> 01:03:31.791
I have made many mistakes towards you!

918
01:03:38.333 --> 01:03:39.416
[giggling]

919
01:03:39.500 --> 01:03:42.125
Slowly, come here.

920
01:03:42.208 --> 01:03:45.625
[giggling] Watch out, there are stairs!

921
01:03:45.708 --> 01:03:48.208
-Slowly.
-Be careful!

922
01:03:48.708 --> 01:03:50.416
Be careful.

923
01:03:51.750 --> 01:03:53.416
Get ready!

924
01:03:53.500 --> 01:03:56.083
1,2,3…

925
01:03:59.208 --> 01:04:01.250
Honey, what is this?

926
01:04:02.791 --> 01:04:05.625
Now, Honey, you don't have
to push the bike anymore.

927
01:04:07.791 --> 01:04:10.375
This is really for me?

928
01:04:11.166 --> 01:04:12.208
Of course!

929
01:04:12.291 --> 01:04:14.041
Honey, but this is so expensive.

930
01:04:14.125 --> 01:04:17.625
I have a payment plan for it.

931
01:04:19.083 --> 01:04:24.083
Thank God, I was accepted
into SD Nusa Indah.

932
01:04:24.166 --> 01:04:25.125
For real?

933
01:04:26.333 --> 01:04:28.833
[shouting] Thank God
Congratulations, Honey!

934
01:04:28.916 --> 01:04:32.791
[both laughing]

935
01:04:32.875 --> 01:04:35.500
Masya Allah, Congratulations, Honey!

936
01:04:35.583 --> 01:04:36.416
[giggles]

937
01:04:36.500 --> 01:04:39.208
I'll take the old one to the shop later,
so you can use it daily!

938
01:04:40.166 --> 01:04:42.583
Wait b-but, I’m sorry Honey…

939
01:04:42.666 --> 01:04:46.166
It's still registered in my name,
since I used my ID to do it yesterday.

940
01:04:46.250 --> 01:04:50.458
-It's okay, Honey.
-Just try it.

941
01:04:50.541 --> 01:04:51.541
Come with me!

942
01:04:52.625 --> 01:04:53.750
-Let’s go!
-[quiet grunt]

943
01:04:54.541 --> 01:04:55.875
Why aren't you holding me? Hold on to me!

944
01:04:56.833 --> 01:04:58.083
[both laughing]

945
01:04:58.166 --> 01:05:01.875
Yay, new bike!

946
01:05:01.958 --> 01:05:04.000
[Irfan] I have a surprise for you too.

947
01:05:04.750 --> 01:05:07.208
Let's have a Honeymoon
before you start working.

948
01:05:07.291 --> 01:05:11.791
[ocean surf]

949
01:05:13.375 --> 01:05:20.083
[swelling music]

950
01:05:35.416 --> 01:05:37.166
[laughing loudly]

951
01:05:37.250 --> 01:05:41.375
[excited scream]

952
01:05:51.041 --> 01:05:51.958
[scanner beeps]

953
01:05:54.625 --> 01:05:55.625
Let's buy some snacks.

954
01:05:55.708 --> 01:05:57.375
-[cell phone buzzes]
-Honey, it's Dad.

955
01:05:57.458 --> 01:05:58.333
Pick it up.

956
01:05:59.916 --> 01:06:00.916
Peace be upon you.

957
01:06:11.833 --> 01:06:17.000
[quiet music]

958
01:06:55.916 --> 01:06:59.958
[sniffing]

959
01:07:06.791 --> 01:07:07.625
Honey, what are you doing?

960
01:07:07.708 --> 01:07:08.666
Mom?

961
01:07:08.750 --> 01:07:10.208
[startled breath]

962
01:07:16.041 --> 01:07:20.791
[soft music]

963
01:07:25.916 --> 01:07:26.916
Are you done?

964
01:07:28.000 --> 01:07:28.875
I am.

965
01:07:28.958 --> 01:07:29.833
Let's go.

966
01:07:34.166 --> 01:07:35.458
[Norma] What's wrong?

967
01:07:35.541 --> 01:07:37.125
[Irfan] Nothing!

968
01:07:37.208 --> 01:07:39.041
-Let's grab lunch first, okay?
-Let's go.

969
01:07:43.708 --> 01:07:49.791
-[thoughtful background music]
-[ocean surf]

970
01:08:07.000 --> 01:08:09.541
Honey, you look so beautiful!

971
01:08:20.500 --> 01:08:23.458
[happy giggle]

972
01:08:42.375 --> 01:08:48.208
[light music]

973
01:09:06.208 --> 01:09:11.375
[thoughtfull music]

974
01:09:14.583 --> 01:09:15.708
What’s wrong?

975
01:09:18.291 --> 01:09:19.416
Nothing, Honey.

976
01:09:30.416 --> 01:09:35.791
[soft erie music]

977
01:09:45.458 --> 01:09:46.458
What’s wrong?

978
01:09:47.625 --> 01:09:48.458
[Norma] Honey?

979
01:09:52.000 --> 01:09:52.916
[confused umm]

980
01:09:54.208 --> 01:09:57.791
Let's go to sleep, Honey.
I think I'm not well.

981
01:10:06.541 --> 01:10:08.791
-Peace be upon you.
-Peace be upon you.

982
01:10:08.875 --> 01:10:13.083
Peace be upon you. Wow, perfect timing…

983
01:10:13.166 --> 01:10:15.291
I'd like to take my leave.

984
01:10:16.583 --> 01:10:20.458
Dad, you better go to Jakarta tomorrow,
or you'll arrive late.

985
01:10:20.541 --> 01:10:24.916
It's fine, because we have
many things coming tomorrow.

986
01:10:25.000 --> 01:10:28.125
Koh Akin tends to get confused
when Dad isn't around.

987
01:10:28.708 --> 01:10:29.583
Let me take you, Dad?

988
01:10:29.666 --> 01:10:32.000
No need, I've already
booked a travel agency.

989
01:10:33.458 --> 01:10:37.541
[footsteps]

990
01:10:37.625 --> 01:10:38.666
Mom.

991
01:10:45.666 --> 01:10:50.750
[soft dramatic music]

992
01:10:59.041 --> 01:11:02.750
-That looks like the travel agency.
-Oh yes, it is!

993
01:11:03.458 --> 01:11:05.291
-I'll go get my bag first.
-I'll get it for you, Dad.

994
01:11:05.958 --> 01:11:06.791
Okay.

995
01:11:09.958 --> 01:11:13.833
-How was the trip?
-[chuckle] It was good.

996
01:11:26.333 --> 01:11:27.333
Mom…

997
01:11:30.958 --> 01:11:33.208
Next time you go on vacation,
please take me along, okay?

998
01:11:33.291 --> 01:11:35.750
[giggle] Please stop it, Dad!

999
01:11:35.833 --> 01:11:37.916
Honey, they're already waiting.

1000
01:11:39.500 --> 01:11:40.500
Yes, Honey.

1001
01:11:42.583 --> 01:11:45.833
It turns out the travel vehicle is small.

1002
01:11:46.416 --> 01:11:47.291
Dad.

1003
01:11:47.375 --> 01:11:49.250
Alright, thank you Irfan.

1004
01:11:49.333 --> 01:11:50.291
[short sigh]

1005
01:11:55.250 --> 01:12:01.041
I give all my care to Norma,
she's my only beloved girl.

1006
01:12:01.125 --> 01:12:02.541
[murmer of assent]

1007
01:12:02.625 --> 01:12:03.750
I promise you, Dad.

1008
01:12:09.625 --> 01:12:11.500
Aren't you going to
say goodbye to Mom first?

1009
01:12:11.583 --> 01:12:14.333
Please tell Mom that I've taken my leave.

1010
01:12:21.708 --> 01:12:25.125
I thought the travel van was big enough.

1011
01:12:26.333 --> 01:12:29.666
-[van driver] Will it fit?
-[Dad] Of course, I'm slim.

1012
01:12:30.166 --> 01:12:35.166
Well, tell the ceiling repairman
where it needs to be fixed!

1013
01:12:35.250 --> 01:12:37.375
Why couldn’t you fix a
piece of cake like this?

1014
01:12:37.458 --> 01:12:38.375
[frustrated moan]

1015
01:12:39.750 --> 01:12:40.625
Rina?

1016
01:12:41.291 --> 01:12:43.916
I'd like to go home now,
I need to wait for the ceiling repairman.

1017
01:12:44.000 --> 01:12:45.958
Yahya is unreliable!

1018
01:12:46.583 --> 01:12:50.708
[deep sigh] He tends
to follow people, like a spy…

1019
01:12:50.791 --> 01:12:53.666
-But he can't even wait for a repairman.
-[customer] Are they done, Ma'am?

1020
01:12:54.458 --> 01:12:56.500
-Thank you. You're welcome.
-It's the right amount.

1021
01:13:07.000 --> 01:13:09.041
MIERINA CHICKEN NODDLES

1022
01:13:09.125 --> 01:13:11.791
ON A BREAK

1023
01:13:19.583 --> 01:13:21.208
Is my order ready, Mom?

1024
01:13:30.791 --> 01:13:33.291
My friends miss your chicken noodles.

1025
01:13:37.833 --> 01:13:39.208
I also miss it.

1026
01:13:46.166 --> 01:13:50.000
What happened to you yesterday? Tell me!

1027
01:13:51.791 --> 01:13:53.625
We shouldn't have done that.

1028
01:13:53.708 --> 01:13:54.958
[light sigh]

1029
01:13:55.625 --> 01:13:59.958
-[pensive music]
-[door closes behind]

1030
01:14:02.166 --> 01:14:03.875
-[panting]
-[door slams]

1031
01:14:08.833 --> 01:14:10.291
Why do you keep avoiding me?

1032
01:14:10.958 --> 01:14:12.791
Is it just me who's feeling this?

1033
01:14:14.125 --> 01:14:16.208
You are my son!

1034
01:14:17.125 --> 01:14:19.625
[deep breath] Don't make my mind a mess!

1035
01:14:20.375 --> 01:14:21.833
[breathing]

1036
01:14:31.500 --> 01:14:34.166
If I had a choice,
I wouldn't feel this either.

1037
01:14:36.583 --> 01:14:38.041
[quiet grunt]

1038
01:14:41.250 --> 01:14:43.916
[shallow breathing]

1039
01:14:53.541 --> 01:14:57.291
[labored breathing]

1040
01:14:57.375 --> 01:15:00.375
[music swells]

1041
01:15:00.458 --> 01:15:01.875
OPEN

1042
01:15:01.958 --> 01:15:03.125
Shit!

1043
01:15:06.000 --> 01:15:10.250
Because of Yahya, I left my wallet behind.

1044
01:15:10.333 --> 01:15:13.583
Dumb, dumb, really dumb!

1045
01:15:15.458 --> 01:15:16.708
What? "Break"?

1046
01:15:18.208 --> 01:15:19.375
Closed?

1047
01:15:19.458 --> 01:15:23.125
[banging on door with force]

1048
01:15:23.208 --> 01:15:27.166
[labored breathing]

1049
01:15:29.958 --> 01:15:31.375
The "order" is done, right?

1050
01:15:31.458 --> 01:15:32.583
Rina?

1051
01:15:35.083 --> 01:15:35.916
Rina?

1052
01:15:36.708 --> 01:15:39.583
What should I do now, huh?

1053
01:15:41.875 --> 01:15:44.750
-[frightened gasp]
-[wall impact sound]

1054
01:15:46.541 --> 01:15:49.000
[Auntie] What's the fight about?

1055
01:15:51.625 --> 01:15:53.541
-What's that thumping sound?
-[pounding noise]

1056
01:15:56.875 --> 01:15:58.500
Ouch! I'm stuck!

1057
01:15:58.583 --> 01:16:01.208
Rina, Rina, what happened?

1058
01:16:02.250 --> 01:16:04.583
-There is a rat!
-What? A rat?

1059
01:16:04.666 --> 01:16:07.958
-[Mom] There is a rat!
-What, where is it?

1060
01:16:08.041 --> 01:16:11.541
-There’s a big rat
-Oh my! I’m scared of rats!

1061
01:16:11.625 --> 01:16:14.708
-That’s the rat, Auntie. Wanna see?
-[frightened squeal] No, no, thanks.

1062
01:16:14.791 --> 01:16:16.916
Get rid of it, Irfan. I'm afraid.

1063
01:16:17.000 --> 01:16:21.291
[gasping]

1064
01:16:21.375 --> 01:16:22.416
Oh my God!

1065
01:16:24.666 --> 01:16:25.750
[motorcylce engine]

1066
01:16:29.000 --> 01:16:33.458
[dramatic music]

1067
01:16:42.333 --> 01:16:44.416
[door closing]

1068
01:16:44.500 --> 01:16:46.791
Norma has been asleep,
and I just want to tell you…

1069
01:16:46.875 --> 01:16:50.208
You can avoid me after this, it's okay,
but please give me a moment.

1070
01:16:50.291 --> 01:16:51.416
[sobbing]

1071
01:16:51.500 --> 01:16:53.125
I can't forget what happened yesterday.

1072
01:16:53.208 --> 01:16:54.291
[quiet sobbing]

1073
01:16:58.708 --> 01:16:59.833
Now what?

1074
01:17:02.958 --> 01:17:04.291
What do we do now?

1075
01:17:04.375 --> 01:17:05.625
[short breath]

1076
01:17:07.458 --> 01:17:09.250
I can't keep going on like this.

1077
01:17:29.708 --> 01:17:32.041
No one asked you to keep doing this.

1078
01:17:36.208 --> 01:17:37.750
Get out!

1079
01:17:46.000 --> 01:17:47.166
Look at me!

1080
01:17:47.250 --> 01:17:53.375
[quiet music]

1081
01:17:54.375 --> 01:17:55.250
[labored breath]

1082
01:17:58.333 --> 01:18:01.416
Tell me you don't feel what I feel.

1083
01:18:07.500 --> 01:18:09.250
Now what should we do?

1084
01:18:19.541 --> 01:18:21.458
[Irfan] Be honest with our feelings.

1085
01:18:30.541 --> 01:18:32.916
[gasping]

1086
01:18:38.375 --> 01:18:39.583
[gasping]

1087
01:18:41.000 --> 01:18:42.625
[bumping sound]

1088
01:18:43.458 --> 01:18:46.125
[dramatic music]

1089
01:18:56.166 --> 01:18:57.208
Mom?

1090
01:19:07.666 --> 01:19:08.750
[passionate kiss]

1091
01:19:08.833 --> 01:19:13.458
[dramatic music]

1092
01:19:21.000 --> 01:19:22.083
Mom?

1093
01:19:26.958 --> 01:19:28.208
[door knock]

1094
01:19:32.625 --> 01:19:34.041
Can I come in?

1095
01:19:34.125 --> 01:19:40.000
[music swells]

1096
01:19:43.291 --> 01:19:44.166
[door opens]

1097
01:19:53.166 --> 01:19:54.208
Are you okay?

1098
01:19:56.083 --> 01:19:57.333
It's nothing.

1099
01:19:59.875 --> 01:20:01.208
I'm just tired.

1100
01:20:02.291 --> 01:20:04.333
[light sigh]

1101
01:20:04.416 --> 01:20:08.375
Of course you're tired, Mom,
the stall has been so busy.

1102
01:20:08.458 --> 01:20:10.166
You haven’t had any rest.

1103
01:20:10.666 --> 01:20:14.541
Should I give you a massage
since Irfan will be coming late?

1104
01:20:14.625 --> 01:20:18.041
No thanks. You just go to sleep.

1105
01:20:18.125 --> 01:20:21.041
Tomorrow is your first day, right?

1106
01:20:21.125 --> 01:20:22.041
[quiet sigh]

1107
01:20:25.458 --> 01:20:27.583
Go on, go back to your room.

1108
01:20:29.250 --> 01:20:30.750
Well, okay.

1109
01:20:31.875 --> 01:20:33.875
Call me when you need me.

1110
01:20:40.958 --> 01:20:42.125
[footsteps]

1111
01:20:42.208 --> 01:20:43.916
[quiet breath]

1112
01:20:44.000 --> 01:20:44.916
[door closes]

1113
01:21:00.500 --> 01:21:02.583
[quiet sob]

1114
01:21:05.333 --> 01:21:07.875
[Irfan] Peace be upon you, Honey.
I’m home

1115
01:21:07.958 --> 01:21:11.875
-[Irfan] Peace be upon you.
-Why didn’t you sleep yet?

1116
01:21:11.958 --> 01:21:14.166
[Irfan] Are you waiting for me?

1117
01:21:14.250 --> 01:21:15.833
Come and hug me, Honey!

1118
01:21:15.916 --> 01:21:18.041
[muted voices]

1119
01:21:18.750 --> 01:21:20.958
[Norma] Aren't
you tired? Have you eaten yet?

1120
01:21:21.041 --> 01:21:23.291
[Irfan] I haven't eaten, actually.

1121
01:21:23.375 --> 01:21:26.375
[Norma] Do you want to cook,
or do you want me to cook for you?

1122
01:21:30.791 --> 01:21:31.958
Honey…

1123
01:21:33.000 --> 01:21:36.333
Let's eat first.
I've cooked some fried milkfish.

1124
01:21:36.875 --> 01:21:38.833
Just pack a lunch for me, Honey.
It's getting late.

1125
01:21:48.083 --> 01:21:51.500
-Where’s Mom?
-She’s been leaving too early…

1126
01:21:53.500 --> 01:21:55.625
…and taking a bath so early.

1127
01:21:55.708 --> 01:21:58.666
She said, she went to the market first
before going to the stall.

1128
01:21:59.375 --> 01:22:00.666
Is this rice enough for you?

1129
01:22:03.791 --> 01:22:05.500
I made it special for you!

1130
01:22:06.958 --> 01:22:08.166
[kissing sound]

1131
01:22:09.166 --> 01:22:11.666
-Peace be upon you.
-Peace be upon you.

1132
01:22:13.375 --> 01:22:18.625
[dramatic music]

1133
01:22:21.583 --> 01:22:25.041
ON A BREAK

1134
01:22:47.250 --> 01:22:53.000
[dramatic music swells]

1135
01:22:57.833 --> 01:23:00.541
[beads clattering]

1136
01:23:11.125 --> 01:23:12.083
[phone keypad clicking]

1137
01:23:14.708 --> 01:23:15.875
-[door opening]
-[quiet sigh]

1138
01:23:18.791 --> 01:23:19.791
Honey.

1139
01:23:28.458 --> 01:23:32.833
I think it's time we had a baby.

1140
01:23:43.666 --> 01:23:45.375
Can we skip it for tonight?

1141
01:23:46.958 --> 01:23:48.583
I have to leave very early tomorrow.

1142
01:23:48.666 --> 01:23:52.625
[soft thoughtful music]

1143
01:23:53.291 --> 01:23:54.916
[short sigh]

1144
01:23:55.000 --> 01:23:56.000
Honey…

1145
01:23:57.541 --> 01:23:58.583
It's okay, right?

1146
01:23:59.833 --> 01:24:00.666
Hmm.

1147
01:24:03.166 --> 01:24:06.208
-[frustrated sigh]
-[covers moving]

1148
01:24:09.541 --> 01:24:16.041
[mysterious music]

1149
01:24:27.833 --> 01:24:29.916
Why did he come back so early?

1150
01:24:37.125 --> 01:24:38.166
What?

1151
01:24:38.250 --> 01:24:39.666
[gasping]

1152
01:24:39.750 --> 01:24:41.625
Let's stop now, she will be home soon.

1153
01:24:43.166 --> 01:24:45.833
It's 2 p.m.
We still have two hours left, right?

1154
01:24:46.791 --> 01:24:48.041
[giggles]

1155
01:24:48.125 --> 01:24:49.916
-Here you go!
-Thank you.

1156
01:24:50.000 --> 01:24:52.375
Thanks, you’re welcome.

1157
01:24:55.958 --> 01:24:58.791
-Peace be upon you.
-Peace be upon you.

1158
01:24:58.875 --> 01:25:01.041
-Where are you coming from, Irfan?
-Back from the office, Auntie.

1159
01:25:01.625 --> 01:25:03.500
I'd like a chicken noodle,
I'm really hungry!

1160
01:25:03.583 --> 01:25:04.583
Okay.

1161
01:25:04.666 --> 01:25:07.375
How come your hair is so wet?
Where were you in the rain?

1162
01:25:07.458 --> 01:25:11.083
[embarrassed laugh] I did my wudu,
I’m a good boy, Auntie.

1163
01:25:13.500 --> 01:25:17.833
Of course, a good boy,
you must do 'wudu’ a lot!

1164
01:25:27.083 --> 01:25:30.916
-[moaning sounds]
-[bed creaking]

1165
01:25:33.291 --> 01:25:34.250
[gasp] That’s it!

1166
01:25:35.125 --> 01:25:36.875
It’s over there!

1167
01:25:36.958 --> 01:25:38.208
[pulling hair] Where?

1168
01:25:39.916 --> 01:25:41.041
There!

1169
01:25:41.541 --> 01:25:44.791
[soft supenseful music]

1170
01:25:44.875 --> 01:25:47.291
Here!

1171
01:25:47.375 --> 01:25:48.875
-Inside the room?
-Yes!

1172
01:25:48.958 --> 01:25:50.125
Let me check.

1173
01:25:53.666 --> 01:25:55.458
-I couldn't see!
-You can't see it?

1174
01:25:58.416 --> 01:26:00.166
-No, no!
-[shushing]

1175
01:26:00.750 --> 01:26:01.791
They won’t notice!

1176
01:26:02.375 --> 01:26:06.000
-[giggling]
-[bed moving]

1177
01:26:06.083 --> 01:26:08.583
[gasping]

1178
01:26:12.000 --> 01:26:13.208
Hurry!

1179
01:26:13.291 --> 01:26:14.833
-Do you see anything?
-[shushing] Shut up!

1180
01:26:18.666 --> 01:26:23.208
[moaning sounds]

1181
01:26:25.541 --> 01:26:28.458
-[whisper] I heard a woman's voice.
-[whisper] What was it?

1182
01:26:28.541 --> 01:26:30.541
[moaning] "Ah… oh…"

1183
01:26:30.625 --> 01:26:32.375
-Oh, really?
-Stop…

1184
01:26:32.458 --> 01:26:35.666
Record, please record!

1185
01:26:37.666 --> 01:26:42.041
[giggling]

1186
01:26:44.000 --> 01:26:45.083
Tell me later!

1187
01:26:45.166 --> 01:26:46.291
[shushing]

1188
01:26:55.333 --> 01:26:58.666
[dramatic music building]

1189
01:26:58.750 --> 01:26:59.916
Hurry!

1190
01:27:01.333 --> 01:27:03.000
Oh, great, it fell!

1191
01:27:03.083 --> 01:27:03.958
Shush!

1192
01:27:04.791 --> 01:27:06.583
-What was it?
-[shush]

1193
01:27:07.375 --> 01:27:08.583
Oh my God!

1194
01:27:09.708 --> 01:27:11.500
What are you doing?

1195
01:27:11.583 --> 01:27:12.416
Rina.

1196
01:27:13.416 --> 01:27:16.916
Washing, uh, cleaning the phone screen.

1197
01:27:17.000 --> 01:27:20.416
It was oily before and Auntie ask me
to clean it.

1198
01:27:20.500 --> 01:27:22.250
Did I ask you like that, huh?

1199
01:27:22.333 --> 01:27:27.583
Look, there's a woman's voice
inside Irfan's room.

1200
01:27:27.666 --> 01:27:30.458
-"Ah… Oh…" Right?
-Ah ah

1201
01:27:30.541 --> 01:27:32.208
Let's bust them!

1202
01:27:32.291 --> 01:27:33.875
Auntie!

1203
01:27:33.958 --> 01:27:36.500
He must be doing it with that Etni!

1204
01:27:36.583 --> 01:27:39.791
My intuition is always right,
I'm telling you!

1205
01:27:40.500 --> 01:27:41.916
Where is his room?

1206
01:27:42.000 --> 01:27:43.583
This one right?

1207
01:27:44.083 --> 01:27:46.291
Irfan, get out here!

1208
01:27:46.375 --> 01:27:49.000
-Irfan!
-Come out!

1209
01:27:49.083 --> 01:27:52.333
If you don't come out,
I'm breaking down this door!

1210
01:27:52.416 --> 01:27:53.791
-Break this door!
-[deep sigh]

1211
01:27:54.416 --> 01:27:55.500
Irfan!

1212
01:27:55.583 --> 01:27:56.541
-[deep breath]
-[kicking door]

1213
01:28:04.333 --> 01:28:05.416
[covers moving]

1214
01:28:08.041 --> 01:28:09.166
What’s wrong?

1215
01:28:09.916 --> 01:28:12.333
-Who is in here?
-Who?

1216
01:28:12.958 --> 01:28:13.791
It’s me.

1217
01:28:13.875 --> 01:28:18.166
Yahya and I heard a woman's voice, right?

1218
01:28:18.833 --> 01:28:20.916
-A woman?
-Find out!

1219
01:28:22.708 --> 01:28:23.916
Open all the cupboards!

1220
01:28:27.125 --> 01:28:28.333
Under the bed.

1221
01:28:31.625 --> 01:28:33.000
What is happening here, Auntie?

1222
01:28:33.541 --> 01:28:34.458
Auntie.

1223
01:28:36.875 --> 01:28:39.625
Why do you always come home at lunchtime?

1224
01:28:40.458 --> 01:28:43.916
With a one-hour break,
am I not allowed to rest at home?

1225
01:28:44.000 --> 01:28:46.458
[gritting teeth] I know
you're hiding something…

1226
01:28:46.541 --> 01:28:48.625
…even Yahya heard a woman's voice here.

1227
01:28:48.708 --> 01:28:50.291
It's kind of unclear though.

1228
01:28:50.375 --> 01:28:51.666
Let’s look out outside!

1229
01:28:51.750 --> 01:28:52.583
Let’s go!

1230
01:28:53.458 --> 01:28:55.041
[Auntie] Watch out,
I'm definitely going to find her.

1231
01:28:55.125 --> 01:28:59.208
If we find her, I won't forgive you.
Let's go!

1232
01:28:59.291 --> 01:29:01.083
Let's search out front.

1233
01:29:01.166 --> 01:29:02.541
[Yahya] Can I check up in the bathroom?

1234
01:29:02.625 --> 01:29:04.625
[Auntie] Find her!

1235
01:29:04.708 --> 01:29:06.958
Where is she?

1236
01:29:07.041 --> 01:29:09.458
[Yahya] I've looked
everywhere and found nothing.

1237
01:29:09.541 --> 01:29:11.416
Then where is she?

1238
01:29:11.500 --> 01:29:16.000
How about we go back in and apologize now.

1239
01:29:16.083 --> 01:29:18.083
Hey, why are you dragging me!

1240
01:29:18.166 --> 01:29:19.916
Sorry for causing trouble.

1241
01:29:20.000 --> 01:29:22.500
She wants to apologize
because we misheard a voice.

1242
01:29:22.583 --> 01:29:24.875
You're acting like a child!

1243
01:29:24.958 --> 01:29:27.291
Sorry for disturbing you,
please go to sleep.

1244
01:29:27.375 --> 01:29:30.791
-Let’s go home Auntie.
-You're acting so childish. You are!

1245
01:29:31.708 --> 01:29:33.833
[Ifran] I've
changed the sheet and blanket.

1246
01:29:34.750 --> 01:29:38.833
I'm sure Irfan is lying,
my gut feeling is really strong!

1247
01:29:38.916 --> 01:29:41.791
Auntie, where is the proof? We have none!

1248
01:29:41.875 --> 01:29:45.500
You did hear the woman's voice
in the room, didn't you?

1249
01:29:46.041 --> 01:29:49.208
Yes, it's really a woman,
but what if it's something else?

1250
01:29:49.291 --> 01:29:51.916
-Don't try to scare me!
-Okay, listen…

1251
01:29:52.000 --> 01:29:55.333
Let's assume your gut is right
and then you tell this to Norma.

1252
01:29:55.416 --> 01:29:59.208
Norma and Irfan get divorced for your gut,
are you willing to bear the sin?

1253
01:29:59.291 --> 01:30:03.041
[perky music]

1254
01:30:03.125 --> 01:30:06.333
It would be better if you focused
on my phone that's totally dead.

1255
01:30:07.125 --> 01:30:08.416
Auntie will buy and replace mine, right?

1256
01:30:08.500 --> 01:30:09.666
[In English] Stop!

1257
01:30:10.708 --> 01:30:14.625
-My gut said it can be fixed, Auntie.
-Fix it yourself, then!

1258
01:30:14.708 --> 01:30:15.750
Excuse me.

1259
01:30:16.833 --> 01:30:17.708
[short sigh]

1260
01:30:18.500 --> 01:30:21.625
-[giggle] The whole house? Seriously?
-Indeed!

1261
01:30:21.708 --> 01:30:23.791
-"Admit it! Where is she?"
-[laughing]

1262
01:30:23.875 --> 01:30:26.291
"Yahya, check all the cupboards
and under the bed"

1263
01:30:26.375 --> 01:30:30.791
And she said, "Why do you always
come home at lunchtime?"

1264
01:30:30.875 --> 01:30:34.458
I just said,
"It's a one-hour break, Auntie."

1265
01:30:34.541 --> 01:30:37.000
Am I not allowed to rest at home, right?

1266
01:30:39.083 --> 01:30:43.791
-Would you like a tea?
-Yes, thank you, Honey.

1267
01:30:52.041 --> 01:30:54.875
-What happened, Honey?
-Nothing.

1268
01:30:59.458 --> 01:31:01.958
-Who passed away?
-Putri.

