01:50:42.208 --> 01:50:45.000
How disgusting to have a boss like that…

1530
01:50:45.083 --> 01:50:46.708
I never expected it!

1531
01:50:46.791 --> 01:50:48.458
I can't believe it.

1532
01:50:52.291 --> 01:50:55.500
Ew, I hope the new
manager isn't like this.

1533
01:50:59.250 --> 01:51:04.208
[background noises]

1534
01:51:11.416 --> 01:51:13.583
[faint sigh]

1535
01:51:15.500 --> 01:51:16.666
Thank you, Dad…

1536
01:51:17.500 --> 01:51:18.875
…for accompanying me.

1537
01:51:19.458 --> 01:51:23.166
Maybe if you weren't here…

1538
01:51:25.333 --> 01:51:27.125
…I would be alone.

1539
01:51:27.208 --> 01:51:31.458
[soft music]

1540
01:51:32.833 --> 01:51:34.583
I would go crazy.

1541
01:51:38.416 --> 01:51:41.041
[sniffling]

1542
01:51:48.166 --> 01:51:52.916
-Please forgive me!
-You didn’t do anything, Dad!

1543
01:51:53.916 --> 01:51:57.833
You've never truly felt
what it's like to have a mother, Dear.

1544
01:51:57.916 --> 01:52:00.458
-Oh my God! Dad.
-I’m so sorry.

1545
01:52:00.541 --> 01:52:04.541
Dad, this is not your fault!

1546
01:52:04.625 --> 01:52:08.291
I failed to keep you both safe.

1547
01:52:10.000 --> 01:52:12.541
-I can’t respect your Mom.
-No!

1548
01:52:12.625 --> 01:52:15.166
-I can’t take care of you.
-No, you're wrong!

1549
01:52:15.250 --> 01:52:19.458
If only I had stayed here, Dear,
none of this would have happened.

1550
01:52:19.541 --> 01:52:23.083
Please don’t say that!

1551
01:52:23.166 --> 01:52:26.416
A good mother won’t cheat, Dad.

1552
01:52:28.375 --> 01:52:31.583
[crying] She would never betray, never!

1553
01:52:33.541 --> 01:52:35.791
Even if her husband isn't home.

1554
01:52:36.458 --> 01:52:40.541
So, there's no need to say sorry.
You didn't do anything wrong.

1555
01:52:41.375 --> 01:52:42.666
Do you know

1556
01:52:44.833 --> 01:52:48.916
why I feel guilty towards you, Dear?

1557
01:52:50.458 --> 01:52:56.166
[Dad] Actually, I already suspected
that Mom liked Irfan.

1558
01:52:59.791 --> 01:53:02.541
But I couldn't bring myself
to tell you, Dear.

1559
01:53:05.208 --> 01:53:06.916
I also didn't expect…

1560
01:53:07.958 --> 01:53:11.791
…that your husband had the
same feelings towards your Mom.

1561
01:53:12.666 --> 01:53:16.458
-It’s my fault, Dear.
-Stop, stop it, Dad!

1562
01:53:16.541 --> 01:53:22.166
-I’m really sorry, my Dear.
-Stop it, Dad!

1563
01:53:23.250 --> 01:53:24.458
[Ummi] Dear…

1564
01:53:24.541 --> 01:53:27.291
Do you remember what I taught you before?

1565
01:53:27.791 --> 01:53:31.666
Trust in God with all your heart.

1566
01:53:32.250 --> 01:53:37.500
God does not burden a soul
beyond what it can bear.

1567
01:53:37.583 --> 01:53:39.791
[sobbing] Well, I know…

1568
01:53:40.583 --> 01:53:42.750
You might be sad today.

1569
01:53:43.625 --> 01:53:44.791
But…

1570
01:53:48.541 --> 01:53:53.250
…you should know that you’re not alone.

1571
01:53:55.583 --> 01:53:58.291
It's going to be okay.

1572
01:53:58.375 --> 01:54:01.583
God will not leave you.

1573
01:54:02.875 --> 01:54:03.875
Okay?

1574
01:54:04.916 --> 01:54:05.916
[retching]

1575
01:54:06.000 --> 01:54:09.500
[Norma] Right now, I only feel hate…

1576
01:54:11.750 --> 01:54:17.416
mad, mad at myself.

1577
01:54:22.416 --> 01:54:26.125
Why am I so stupid, Ummi?

1578
01:54:26.208 --> 01:54:29.250
I can't bear to see Mom anymore!

1579
01:54:29.333 --> 01:54:34.375
I don't know how to see her the same.

1580
01:54:34.458 --> 01:54:37.250
[Ummi] You can hate her actions,

1581
01:54:37.333 --> 01:54:41.000
but please don’t hate your own mother.

1582
01:54:41.083 --> 01:54:45.000
What matters most now is
that you pray to God…

1583
01:54:45.083 --> 01:54:47.125
Ask Allah in prayer…

1584
01:54:49.083 --> 01:54:53.250
To help you overcome self-hatred.

1585
01:55:13.166 --> 01:55:17.208
[rustling in garbage]

1586
01:55:18.458 --> 01:55:19.333
[gasp]

1587
01:55:19.416 --> 01:55:24.583
[quiet thoughtful music]

1588
01:55:49.958 --> 01:55:56.041
[louder music]

1589
01:55:56.125 --> 01:55:57.666
[retching]

1590
01:55:59.250 --> 01:56:02.083
[deep breath]

1591
01:56:18.916 --> 01:56:24.833
[sobbing]

1592
01:56:33.750 --> 01:56:39.500
[thoughtful music continues]

1593
01:56:54.500 --> 01:57:00.291
[deep crying]

1594
01:57:37.833 --> 01:57:42.583
[eerie music building]

1595
01:57:52.791 --> 01:57:53.708
Mom…

1596
01:57:58.041 --> 01:57:59.083
Mom,

1597
01:58:00.791 --> 01:58:02.625
I saw Irfan's bike outside…

1598
01:58:02.708 --> 01:58:04.333
Where is he now?

1599
01:58:05.708 --> 01:58:08.750
[crying] Where is he now? Mom, tell me!

1600
01:58:08.833 --> 01:58:11.000
Tell me! Where is he now?

1601
01:58:11.083 --> 01:58:12.583
[sobbing]

1602
01:58:14.083 --> 01:58:15.333
Are you all insane?

1603
01:58:15.416 --> 01:58:16.458
[purse slamming down]

1604
01:58:21.791 --> 01:58:24.166
Irfan!

1605
01:58:26.958 --> 01:58:28.416
-You jerk!
-[loud slap and cry]

1606
01:58:29.375 --> 01:58:32.291
What is it?

1607
01:58:32.875 --> 01:58:33.708
[screaming]

1608
01:58:34.666 --> 01:58:35.916
Irfan!

1609
01:58:36.708 --> 01:58:38.375
Get out!

1610
01:58:38.958 --> 01:58:41.000
[screaming]

1611
01:58:41.083 --> 01:58:43.041
Don't run!

1612
01:58:44.166 --> 01:58:45.333
[Irfan grunting]

1613
01:58:45.875 --> 01:58:47.083
[Norma screaming]

1614
01:58:50.416 --> 01:58:51.791
Don't run!

1615
01:58:54.208 --> 01:58:55.041
[groan of pain]

1616
01:58:55.125 --> 01:58:57.000
[Mom] Irfan, run!

1617
01:58:57.875 --> 01:58:59.000
[fighting and crying]

1618
01:59:02.000 --> 01:59:03.333
[screaming]

1619
01:59:04.416 --> 01:59:05.500
[grunting]

1620
01:59:09.291 --> 01:59:11.958
[dramatic sounds playing]

1621
01:59:15.500 --> 01:59:16.916
[Norma] That’s my bike!

1622
01:59:17.500 --> 01:59:19.166
[shouting] You thief!

1623
01:59:19.250 --> 01:59:20.500
[crying out]

1624
01:59:22.208 --> 01:59:27.750
[dramatic music swelling]

1625
01:59:30.833 --> 01:59:34.083
[motorcycle engine]

1626
01:59:38.166 --> 01:59:39.416
Thief!

1627
01:59:40.375 --> 01:59:42.333
[sobbing]

1628
01:59:44.208 --> 01:59:46.791
Bastard!

1629
01:59:49.791 --> 01:59:51.041
[sobbing]

1630
01:59:52.041 --> 01:59:54.166
[Mom] Norma,
stop throwing clothes like this!

1631
01:59:54.250 --> 01:59:55.416
Disgusting clothes!

1632
01:59:55.500 --> 01:59:56.750
You are all insane!

1633
01:59:56.833 --> 01:59:58.958
[crying]

1634
01:59:59.583 --> 02:00:03.166
[screaming hysterically]

1635
02:00:05.541 --> 02:00:07.458
Stop, stop, stop it!

1636
02:00:11.458 --> 02:00:14.041
[sobbing]

1637
02:00:16.291 --> 02:00:17.125
This one…

1638
02:00:18.250 --> 02:00:22.041
This is what gives you
the right to ruin my life!

1639
02:00:24.708 --> 02:00:27.208
[glass breaking]

1640
02:00:27.291 --> 02:00:30.958
Say 'istighfar'!

1641
02:00:31.041 --> 02:00:32.958
You're the one who should say 'istighfar'!

1642
02:00:33.041 --> 02:00:34.541
[grunting]

1643
02:00:44.875 --> 02:00:46.916
[thunder and rain]

1644
02:00:47.000 --> 02:00:49.791
Please forgive me, O Allah!

1645
02:00:55.666 --> 02:00:57.125
[panting]

1646
02:00:57.208 --> 02:00:58.875
Dear!

1647
02:01:00.750 --> 02:01:03.500
[Dad] Oh my God, Dear!

1648
02:01:03.583 --> 02:01:05.750
What happened?

1649
02:01:05.833 --> 02:01:06.916
What happened to you?

1650
02:01:07.000 --> 02:01:10.541
What happened to you, Dear?

1651
02:01:10.625 --> 02:01:11.833
[coughing]

1652
02:01:11.916 --> 02:01:13.208
Tell me!

1653
02:01:15.416 --> 02:01:22.208
[sobbing] I’ve
said that I will forgive Mom.

1654
02:01:24.250 --> 02:01:29.416
But she slept with Irfan again, Dad!

1655
02:01:30.000 --> 02:01:33.458
[sobbing] Please forgive me, God.

1656
02:01:34.958 --> 02:01:40.916
[sobbing] Oh my God!

1657
02:01:41.000 --> 02:01:44.541
[sudden shock, feeling faint]

1658
02:01:48.041 --> 02:01:49.083
Dad!

1659
02:01:50.416 --> 02:01:53.250
[crying out] Dad!

1660
02:01:53.333 --> 02:01:56.333
Wake up, Dad!

1661
02:01:56.416 --> 02:02:00.375
Dad!

1662
02:02:00.458 --> 02:02:02.833
Help!

1663
02:02:02.916 --> 02:02:04.583
Please wake up, Dad!

1664
02:02:10.625 --> 02:02:11.916
Dad…

1665
02:02:12.000 --> 02:02:14.625
[quiet sobs]

1666
02:02:14.708 --> 02:02:17.166
Please, Dad, get better soon.

1667
02:02:17.833 --> 02:02:21.041
Without you, who will be with me?

1668
02:02:22.166 --> 02:02:24.208
Who will stay for me, Dad?

1669
02:02:26.000 --> 02:02:28.958
Please, get well soon, Dad!

1670
02:02:29.041 --> 02:02:31.416
Don’t leave me alone!

1671
02:02:32.333 --> 02:02:34.125
We should stay strong…

1672
02:02:35.916 --> 02:02:37.666
Please, get well soon, okay?

1673
02:02:46.125 --> 02:02:47.166
Dad?

1674
02:02:50.083 --> 02:02:51.000
Dad?

1675
02:02:53.666 --> 02:02:58.916
Promise me, you will get better okay?

1676
02:03:00.041 --> 02:03:01.875
Please stay strong, Dad!

1677
02:03:03.833 --> 02:03:06.291
[Ummi outside] They have wronged you,

1678
02:03:06.375 --> 02:03:07.916
Dad, please get well soon.

1679
02:03:08.000 --> 02:03:09.583
stole from you,

1680
02:03:10.083 --> 02:03:12.083
lied to you,

1681
02:03:12.708 --> 02:03:14.250
and also hurt you.

1682
02:03:16.000 --> 02:03:18.125
If you want to fight them,

1683
02:03:19.666 --> 02:03:22.500
I will give you all my support.

1684
02:03:24.083 --> 02:03:27.666
Or I will even accompany you, okay?

1685
02:03:32.833 --> 02:03:33.833
[soft sigh]

1686
02:03:33.916 --> 02:03:38.208
[pensive music]

1687
02:03:43.791 --> 02:03:45.250
[in Arabic] Our Lord,

1688
02:03:47.333 --> 02:03:48.625
we have wronged

1689
02:03:51.416 --> 02:03:53.083
ourselves,

1690
02:03:53.875 --> 02:03:56.666
and if You do not forgive us

1691
02:03:57.416 --> 02:03:58.666
and have mercy upon us,

1692
02:03:59.458 --> 02:04:02.458
we will surely be among the losers.

1693
02:04:04.708 --> 02:04:08.000
[sobbing, in Indonesian]
O Allah, please forgive me…

1694
02:04:09.458 --> 02:04:13.125
Please forgive me!

1695
02:04:20.291 --> 02:04:24.250
Give strength to this
servant of Yours, O Allah.

1696
02:04:38.041 --> 02:04:39.458
[reporter] Please
answer my question Mr Irfan?

1697
02:04:39.541 --> 02:04:42.000
[judge] Please, everyone, be quiet!

1698
02:04:42.791 --> 02:04:44.541
[Irfan] You ungrateful wretch!

1699
02:04:44.625 --> 02:04:47.291
If it weren't me,
no one would want to marry you.

1700
02:04:48.000 --> 02:04:51.125
If you know religion, you would forgive
your husband, not go to the police.

1701
02:04:51.208 --> 02:04:52.958
Stay calm!
Excuse me, Sir, we’d like to pass.

1702
02:04:54.000 --> 02:04:56.958
[Dad] One day, when you get married again…

1703
02:04:57.541 --> 02:05:04.458
you better hope your daughter
never feels what mine did.

1704
02:05:05.583 --> 02:05:08.875
So you, as a father,

1705
02:05:09.458 --> 02:05:13.666
won't experience what I did.

1706
02:05:14.250 --> 02:05:16.250
Dad, that's enough.

1707
02:05:16.333 --> 02:05:17.375
[officer] Enough, Sir!

1708
02:05:17.458 --> 02:05:18.833
[sobbing]

1709
02:05:18.916 --> 02:05:20.000
DETAINEE

1710
02:05:20.083 --> 02:05:21.500
Please take off the vest.

1711
02:05:22.625 --> 02:05:23.500
Okay.

1712
02:05:25.000 --> 02:05:26.416
Please take a seat over there.

1713
02:05:35.375 --> 02:05:38.250
[judge]
Today is the pronouncement of the verdict.

1714
02:05:38.333 --> 02:05:44.500
Before the verdict is pronounced, is there
anything to be presented in this trial?

1715
02:05:48.208 --> 02:05:49.291
[Norma] Your Honor?

1716
02:05:54.500 --> 02:05:55.958
With your permission…

1717
02:05:56.625 --> 02:05:59.250
may I speak to the Defendant?

1718
02:05:59.333 --> 02:06:01.500
Please step forward.

1719
02:06:17.958 --> 02:06:19.125
[sobbing] Mom…

1720
02:06:20.458 --> 02:06:22.083
Wherever it is…

1721
02:06:23.583 --> 02:06:25.166
[camera flashing]

1722
02:06:29.708 --> 02:06:32.416
I was born from your womb.

1723
02:06:33.958 --> 02:06:36.458
[Norma] I’m so sorry, Mom.

1724
02:06:38.458 --> 02:06:44.833
If my presence makes you
feel burdened, Mom…

1725
02:06:49.708 --> 02:06:53.833
I hope we can both overcome
these trials of life together.

1726
02:06:57.291 --> 02:07:01.333
[sobbing]

1727
02:07:04.416 --> 02:07:06.000
You are a bad daughter!

1728
02:07:07.666 --> 02:07:10.791
You dare to put your own mom in prison.

1729
02:07:10.875 --> 02:07:15.333
[faint thoughtful music]

1730
02:07:15.416 --> 02:07:18.833
I believe that's enough,
you may return to your seat.

1731
02:07:18.916 --> 02:07:21.541
[judge] The trial is resumed.

1732
02:07:21.625 --> 02:07:25.458
Defendants, please pay attention to all

1733
02:07:25.541 --> 02:07:28.458
that is said during
the reading of the verdict.

1734
02:07:28.541 --> 02:07:29.541
Ready?

1735
02:07:30.583 --> 02:07:36.416
Verdict, In the name of justice
based on the One Almighty God.

1736
02:07:36.500 --> 02:07:40.583
Ruling, Declaring the Defendants…

1737
02:07:40.666 --> 02:07:44.791
Irfan Wardana and Rina Siswanti,

1738
02:07:44.875 --> 02:07:51.541
as mentioned above, are proven legally
and convincingly guilty.

1739
02:07:52.875 --> 02:07:55.125
[gavel striking]

1740
02:07:55.208 --> 02:07:58.041
[dramatic crying]

1741
02:07:58.125 --> 02:08:03.083
[soft pensive music]

1742
02:08:03.166 --> 02:08:05.583
[Mom] Oh my Godness!

1743
02:08:07.750 --> 02:08:09.125
[guard] Rina Siswanti.

1744
02:08:13.000 --> 02:08:14.583
Rina Siswanti, you have a guest.

1745
02:08:15.166 --> 02:08:17.708
[gate opening]

1746
02:08:17.791 --> 02:08:20.625
Please, Ma'am, have a seat.

1747
02:08:45.000 --> 02:08:48.041
I've set aside some money in this, Mom…

1748
02:08:48.583 --> 02:08:49.875
for us to go on Umrah.

1749
02:08:52.375 --> 02:08:54.666
I love you, Mom.

1750
02:08:55.833 --> 02:08:59.083
But I just want to ask you one thing…

1751
02:09:00.416 --> 02:09:02.750
…what did I do to you?

1752
02:09:06.458 --> 02:09:07.583
[deep breath]

1753
02:09:10.583 --> 02:09:11.541
Well…

1754
02:09:13.083 --> 02:09:17.666
This might be the last time
I’m here to meet your needs.

1755
02:09:21.333 --> 02:09:23.291
Behave yourself in prison, okay?

1756
02:09:30.041 --> 02:09:31.458
[Norma] Peace be upon you.

1757
02:09:34.583 --> 02:09:36.375
[Mom] You did nothing wrong.

1758
02:09:39.541 --> 02:09:43.083
I've tried to love you as much as I can.

1759
02:09:47.750 --> 02:09:49.458
But I just can’t…

1760
02:09:54.625 --> 02:09:56.125
…I don’t know why.

1761
02:09:56.875 --> 02:10:01.416
["Tak Sanggup Lagi" by Rossa playing]

1762
02:10:06.250 --> 02:10:07.625
[guard] Let's go back to the room, Ma'am.

1763
02:10:07.708 --> 02:10:10.833
♪ After all this time ♪

1764
02:10:11.750 --> 02:10:16.666
♪ I just realized ♪

1765
02:10:16.750 --> 02:10:18.833
[Norma] I was named Norma.

1766
02:10:19.583 --> 02:10:23.166
so that my life would be beautiful,
conforming to societal norms.

1767
02:10:25.083 --> 02:10:29.666
Until today, I have never hated my mother.

1768
02:10:31.500 --> 02:10:36.916
Even to imagine
what's in her heart and mind…

1769
02:10:38.291 --> 02:10:39.541
…I wouldn't dare.

1770
02:10:41.291 --> 02:10:42.250
But truly…

1771
02:10:44.000 --> 02:10:46.958
…I'm not the one you should pity.

1772
02:10:49.291 --> 02:10:54.250
Some women's wombs are
indeed destined to give birth.

1773
02:10:55.708 --> 02:11:00.416
But, it doesn't mean that they have
been granted a heart of love and mercy.

1774
02:11:02.625 --> 02:11:04.583
My only prayer might be…

1775
02:11:05.958 --> 02:11:10.666
When I get to be a mother,

1776
02:11:11.666 --> 02:11:14.250
I wish to be granted the capacity
to love my child boundlessly.

1777
02:11:14.333 --> 02:11:15.916
Just as God loves me.

1778
02:11:17.000 --> 02:11:23.666
"IT IS ENOUGH OF A SIN
FOR A PERSON THAT NEGLECTS…"

1779
02:11:23.750 --> 02:11:28.666
"…THOSE FOR WHOM HE IS RESPONSIBLE."

1780
02:11:28.750 --> 02:11:31.791
HR AN-NASA'I AND AL-HAKIM

1781
02:11:31.875 --> 02:11:36.166
♪ I admit that now ♪

1782
02:11:37.416 --> 02:11:42.333
♪ You're starting to change ♪

1783
02:11:43.250 --> 02:11:47.708
♪ But my pain ♪

1784
02:11:47.791 --> 02:11:53.625
♪ Is to deep be healed ♪

1785
02:11:54.291 --> 02:11:59.250
♪ I want to erase it all ♪

1786
02:12:00.083 --> 02:12:05.458
♪ All of this hatred ♪

1787
02:12:06.125 --> 02:12:09.958
♪ But I don't think it's possible now ♪

1788
02:12:10.041 --> 02:12:16.375
♪ Let me go ♪

1789
02:12:16.458 --> 02:12:21.625
